Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.67,0:00:58.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Just to get out of bed here, dude.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.11,0:01:01.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I got to get me one of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.89,0:01:03.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I look old-fashioned.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.58,0:02:17.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Go back down, center to the left.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.06,0:02:18.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.87,0:02:20.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Good morning, Doctor.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.53,0:02:22.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi, Doctor.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.09,0:02:23.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.25,0:02:25.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.34,0:02:28.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh-huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.06,0:02:29.38,Default,,0,0,0,,George.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.94,0:02:30.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.00,0:02:36.80,Default,,0,0,0,,This way, Doctor.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.80,0:02:37.58,Default,,0,0,0,,This way, this way, this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.58,0:02:39.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.06,0:02:41.06,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, it's good to see you again.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.37,0:02:42.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.06,0:02:43.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh-huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.65,0:02:47.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.13,0:02:53.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.19,0:02:55.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Greetings from Ken Watnick.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.15,0:02:56.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, hi, thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.30,0:03:02.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Nice to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.06,0:03:03.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Nice to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.62,0:03:06.58,Default,,0,0,0,,L.L. Bean Church.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.97,0:03:10.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.71,0:03:10.97,Default,,0,0,0,,How are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.75,0:03:18.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Doc, smile over here.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.59,0:03:20.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, come over here.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.38,0:03:24.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, my, oh, my.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.43,0:03:43.41,Default,,0,0,0,,That's a great hat.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.59,0:03:43.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.03,0:03:46.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Great hat, great hat.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.96,0:03:48.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.77,0:03:48.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.43,0:04:03.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Merry Christmas, David.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.65,0:04:04.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Merry Christmas.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.22,0:04:04.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Merry Christmas.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.05,0:04:42.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Gloria in excelsis Deo.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.06,0:04:56.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Praise be to thee, O Lord, most high, in whose name we are assembled today.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.52,0:05:09.79,Default,,0,0,0,,The 91st Psalm says that those who...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.10,0:05:13.60,Default,,0,0,0,,...put their faith in me are mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.60,0:05:41.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Krishna says, those who believe in me, God said, we need to make a couple of announcements.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.20,0:06:14.95,Default,,0,0,0,,There's much literature about the obligation of the student to the teacher.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.95,0:06:17.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I turn it around the other way.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.18,0:06:22.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm concerned about the obligation and the promise and responsibility of the teacher
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.24,0:06:23.24,Default,,0,0,0,,to the student.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.24,0:06:24.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm answering the question.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.24,0:06:26.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm answering the question.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.00,0:06:26.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm answering the question.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.12,0:06:26.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm answering the question.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.20,0:06:26.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm answering the question.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.25,0:06:26.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm answering the question.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.32,0:06:26.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm answering the question.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.41,0:06:28.87,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not answerable for all of you, so keep that in mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.69,0:06:36.07,Default,,0,0,0,,You screw up, I'm in trouble, you know what I mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.62,0:06:46.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, we'll get to...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.43,0:06:52.50,Default,,0,0,0,,We have a slide on the obligation of the spiritual teacher to be straightforward, honest, to
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.50,0:06:56.62,Default,,0,0,0,,try to remain as simple as possible, and to be completely transparent.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.42,0:07:05.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Needs nothing, wants nothing from students, has nothing to do with their personal lives,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.51,0:07:09.12,Default,,0,0,0,,doesn't try to control them, doesn't tell them what to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.12,0:07:16.11,Default,,0,0,0,,do, have freedom to come and go, don't have to sign up for anything, no obligations, no
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.11,0:07:28.77,Default,,0,0,0,,oaths. That's a cheerful start, isn't it? All right, we're going to go through, as you
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.77,0:07:36.50,Default,,0,0,0,,know, we have by now over a hundred slides from various lectures. So what we're going
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.50,0:07:47.49,Default,,0,0,0,,to do, how many people here are new? How many people are new? Okay. So I'm going to emphasize
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.49,0:07:53.20,Default,,0,0,0,,the basics then, the basics, and the charts that are farther along in the lecture series
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.20,0:08:00.31,Default,,0,0,0,,are in the books, you know, the calibration of the most famous scientists in history,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.31,0:08:06.13,Default,,0,0,0,,et cetera. Those are all very interesting. But today I really want to cover the basics
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.92,0:08:17.68,Default,,0,0,0,,and a few concepts. And once you, they incorporate them, the rest of them become much easier.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.68,0:08:25.87,Default,,0,0,0,,A couple of very basic premises. I speak from several different experiential backgrounds
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.87,0:08:31.69,Default,,0,0,0,,simultaneously. You know, I practiced psychiatry, psychoanalysis, psychology, et cetera, for
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.69,0:08:39.00,Default,,0,0,0,,fifty years. Had a huge practice. Also had, with the roll calls, rather unusual spiritual
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.00,0:08:41.50,Default,,0,0,0,,experiences starting very young, age, you know, about a year and a half ago. And I've
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.50,0:08:48.55,Default,,0,0,0,,been doing a lot of research, three, and very intense throughout my life, that transform,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.55,0:08:55.72,Default,,0,0,0,,they enter context of existence and reality. Therefore I saw some things differently than
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.72,0:09:02.25,Default,,0,0,0,,other people. And some things I thought were quite useful. And they're incorporated into
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.25,0:09:08.80,Default,,0,0,0,,the lecture series as consciousness research. So we'll also be talking about spiritual reality
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.80,0:09:11.42,Default,,0,0,0,,and consciousness research.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.42,0:09:13.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.13,0:09:21.27,Default,,0,0,0,,The reason for that is mankind has never had the capacity to tell truth from falsehood.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.27,0:09:28.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Here we wander around this planet, for zillions of years, and you can't even tell truth from
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.32,0:09:29.32,Default,,0,0,0,,falsehood.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.32,0:09:40.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Letting a kid loose on the desert with no compass. Good luck.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.51,0:09:49.29,Default,,0,0,0,,How we even survived to where we are today is amazing to me. You know, man has been at
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.29,0:09:50.29,Default,,0,0,0,,war.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.29,0:09:57.75,Default,,0,0,0,,93% of the time. 93% of the time. It's been continuous since I've been born. I was born
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.75,0:10:06.22,Default,,0,0,0,,right after World War I, and it's been one war after another ever since. 7% of the time
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.22,0:10:15.11,Default,,0,0,0,,man wasn't at war, he was probably too sick to plague, or some great catastrophe kept
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.11,0:10:21.69,Default,,0,0,0,,him from his usual business. So, we'll discover why that is. Why is man so warlike? He talks
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.69,0:10:22.69,Default,,0,0,0,,peace, but it's the last straw.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.69,0:10:24.08,Default,,0,0,0,,So, we'll, we'll discover why that is. Why is man so warlike? He talks peace, but it's
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.08,0:10:25.08,Default,,0,0,0,,the last straw.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.08,0:10:32.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Man talks peace, but it's the last thing he wants. Man talks peace, but it's the last
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.69,0:10:42.29,Default,,0,0,0,,thing he wants. Resist. Got that? He talks peace, but he doesn't want it. A threat of
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.29,0:10:54.62,Default,,0,0,0,,peace crashes the stock market and everything else, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.62,0:11:00.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Man talks peace, but he lives by war. And we'll see why that is, because we'll cover
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.67,0:11:01.91,Default,,0,0,0,,that when we discuss the evolution of man.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.91,0:11:02.91,Default,,0,0,0,,The evolution of man. The evolution of man. The evolution of man. The evolution of man.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.91,0:11:08.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Are the evolution of the ego over evolutionary time. And we'll see what the impact of that
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.42,0:11:18.72,Default,,0,0,0,,is on man's brain physiology. Spiritual attention alignment absolutely alters your brain physiology
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.72,0:11:27.16,Default,,0,0,0,,so that you see things and process them differently, understand them differently. At the present
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.16,0:11:33.78,Default,,0,0,0,,time, you know, on the caliber of consciousness, truth starts at 200 and goes up to 1,000.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.78,0:11:36.19,Default,,0,0,0,,That which is not true is 295.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.30,0:11:42.00,Default,,0,0,0,,85% of mankind calibrates below 200 at the present time.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.00,0:11:47.49,Default,,0,0,0,,That should give you more realistic expectations of earthly life.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.49,0:11:56.33,Default,,0,0,0,,So now we have slides.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.33,0:11:59.84,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll start with one we always start with.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.84,0:12:03.84,Default,,0,0,0,,And yes, now what, do you see the same thing on all three screens?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.84,0:12:06.10,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.10,0:12:11.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought maybe I'd have to run back and forth between the screens.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.19,0:12:16.59,Default,,0,0,0,,That's a lucky break.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.59,0:12:20.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't need my kid's gym shoes after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.72,0:12:24.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.53,0:12:28.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, we'll talk about how this came to be.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.57,0:12:33.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I was, as I said, I had a very large clinic.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.08,0:12:36.08,Default,,0,0,0,,We had the most hopeless patients from all over the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.08,0:12:39.12,Default,,0,0,0,,They flew them in from all over the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.12,0:12:42.47,Default,,0,0,0,,And a thousand, we had a thousand new patients a year.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.47,0:12:44.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Extremely hopeless.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.87,0:12:47.46,Default,,0,0,0,,And therefore,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.46,0:12:50.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I used every modality that could possibly help people.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.46,0:12:53.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Acupuncture, nutrition, everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.46,0:12:57.75,Default,,0,0,0,,And each thing that we added made a difference.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.75,0:13:03.23,Default,,0,0,0,,You would take ten hopeless cases and put them on certain kinds of diets.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.23,0:13:05.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Seven of them would cure.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.23,0:13:07.51,Default,,0,0,0,,That left seven to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.51,0:13:10.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Those seven, we would test them for cerebral allergy.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.51,0:13:12.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Four of them, we would find what it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.51,0:13:15.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Four would go. We only got three left.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.51,0:13:17.51,Default,,0,0,0,,And we used kinesiology.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.51,0:13:22.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Kinesiology, which I learned from Diamond, Dr. Diamond.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.89,0:13:29.01,Default,,0,0,0,,So, I was giving a lecture one time on kinesiology.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.01,0:13:33.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Kinesiology is so simple that if you can't understand it,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.01,0:13:41.98,Default,,0,0,0,,you have to leave this audience immediately.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.98,0:13:52.66,Default,,0,0,0,,This is Susan, my right arm.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.66,0:13:55.96,Default,,0,0,0,,She's done many thousands of calibrations.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.96,0:13:57.96,Default,,0,0,0,,She's very quick and fast.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.96,0:13:59.99,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why I use her all the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.99,0:14:02.99,Default,,0,0,0,,She's also inexpensive.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.21,0:14:12.21,Default,,0,0,0,,So, I was teaching kinesiology.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.21,0:14:14.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Things that I learned with George Diamond.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.21,0:14:16.21,Default,,0,0,0,,And I was teaching it to our staff.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.21,0:14:19.00,Default,,0,0,0,,And the first thing we...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.00,0:14:21.24,Default,,0,0,0,,One of the first things that we demonstrated
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.24,0:14:24.24,Default,,0,0,0,,was if you take naive subjects
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.24,0:14:27.24,Default,,0,0,0,,and have them look at fluorescent lights,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.24,0:14:29.24,Default,,0,0,0,,they'll go weak.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.24,0:14:31.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, she's not a naive subject.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.39,0:14:33.39,Default,,0,0,0,,So, we can't use her anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.39,0:14:36.39,Default,,0,0,0,,She can't use you anymore for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.39,0:14:39.39,Default,,0,0,0,,But if you take just ordinary people off the street,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.39,0:14:41.39,Default,,0,0,0,,we've done it with many large audiences.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.39,0:14:44.39,Default,,0,0,0,,We've done it with audiences of a thousand people
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.39,0:14:45.39,Default,,0,0,0,,in New York City.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.39,0:14:48.42,Default,,0,0,0,,And if you take naive people
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.42,0:14:51.42,Default,,0,0,0,,and have them hold out their arm,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.42,0:14:54.42,Default,,0,0,0,,and now I ask them, ask you to resist.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.42,0:14:57.42,Default,,0,0,0,,And I push down with two fingers.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.42,0:15:00.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd say that's about six ounces of pressure, wouldn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.64,0:15:01.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, six ounces.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.64,0:15:02.64,Default,,0,0,0,,And I say, resist.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.64,0:15:03.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.64,0:15:04.64,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.64,0:15:08.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, if you take naive people
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.58,0:15:10.58,Default,,0,0,0,,and have them look at the fluorescent light,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.58,0:15:12.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll put your arm up.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.58,0:15:15.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to hold something in mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.58,0:15:16.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.58,0:15:17.58,Default,,0,0,0,,What I'm holding in mind
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.58,0:15:19.58,Default,,0,0,0,,calibrates over 200 resist.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.58,0:15:20.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.63,0:15:25.99,Default,,0,0,0,,If you have a person look at fluorescent lights,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.99,0:15:27.99,Default,,0,0,0,,their arm will go weak.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.99,0:15:29.99,Default,,0,0,0,,If you hold pesticides over the solar plexus,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.99,0:15:31.99,Default,,0,0,0,,their arm will go weak.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.99,0:15:33.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Sweet and low.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.21,0:15:36.37,Default,,0,0,0,,We used to pass it out to the audience
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.37,0:15:39.37,Default,,0,0,0,,and count it out in twos.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.37,0:15:41.37,Default,,0,0,0,,One's a doctor, one's a patient.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.37,0:15:46.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway, certain things made everybody go weak,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.08,0:15:48.62,Default,,0,0,0,,fluorescent lights especially.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.62,0:15:50.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Think of all the people working all day,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.62,0:15:52.62,Default,,0,0,0,,all their lives under fluorescent lights
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.62,0:15:55.62,Default,,0,0,0,,that are making their energies go weak all day long.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.62,0:15:56.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.62,0:16:01.12,Default,,0,0,0,,So I was demonstrating it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.12,0:16:04.22,Default,,0,0,0,,So that night at the clinic, I said,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.22,0:16:06.22,Default,,0,0,0,,you can sit down.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.22,0:16:08.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I said, I need some volunteers.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.22,0:16:10.27,Default,,0,0,0,,So some people volunteered.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.27,0:16:12.27,Default,,0,0,0,,We had an attitudinal healing center.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.27,0:16:14.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Jerry Jampolsky came over
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.27,0:16:16.27,Default,,0,0,0,,and he started the first one on Tiburon
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.27,0:16:18.75,Default,,0,0,0,,and we had the second one.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.75,0:16:21.75,Default,,0,0,0,,So I said, I need some students
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.75,0:16:24.83,Default,,0,0,0,,to teach a class in kinesiology.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.83,0:16:29.39,Default,,0,0,0,,And they were doing the Course in Miracles.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.39,0:16:33.39,Default,,0,0,0,,And so I said, okay, kid, look at the fluorescent lights
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.39,0:16:35.39,Default,,0,0,0,,and they did not go weak.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.39,0:16:37.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I said, what?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.39,0:16:38.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Look at the lights.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.39,0:16:40.39,Default,,0,0,0,,They did not go weak.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.39,0:16:42.39,Default,,0,0,0,,They did not go weak with pesticides.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.39,0:16:44.82,Default,,0,0,0,,They're sweet and low.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.82,0:16:45.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Something had happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.82,0:16:47.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Something was different about these people
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.82,0:16:49.82,Default,,0,0,0,,who were spiritual students.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.82,0:16:52.82,Default,,0,0,0,,So I started a small research project.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.82,0:16:56.91,Default,,0,0,0,,A number of people just starting the Course in Miracles.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.91,0:16:59.91,Default,,0,0,0,,And I tested them out at the very beginning of the course
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.91,0:17:00.91,Default,,0,0,0,,before they started.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.91,0:17:02.91,Default,,0,0,0,,They all went weak with pesticides.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.91,0:17:05.20,Default,,0,0,0,,They all went weak with fluorescent lights.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.20,0:17:08.20,Default,,0,0,0,,And we retested them about once a week.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.20,0:17:10.20,Default,,0,0,0,,And by the time they got to less than 75,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.20,0:17:13.20,Default,,0,0,0,,around in there, 75, 80, 85,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.20,0:17:16.20,Default,,0,0,0,,all of a sudden they would not go weak to anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.20,0:17:19.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Something had happened to their consciousness
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.55,0:17:21.68,Default,,0,0,0,,that made them immune
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.68,0:17:24.68,Default,,0,0,0,,to the adverse effects of negative stimuli.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.68,0:17:27.68,Default,,0,0,0,,They were no longer subject to what was out there.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.68,0:17:29.68,Default,,0,0,0,,And that was the premise,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.68,0:17:34.34,Default,,0,0,0,,you're only subject to what you hold in mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.34,0:17:36.34,Default,,0,0,0,,It progressed from there then
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.34,0:17:38.34,Default,,0,0,0,,and we discovered a scale of consciousness
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.34,0:17:40.50,Default,,0,0,0,,of one to a thousand.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.50,0:17:42.50,Default,,0,0,0,,And on the scale of consciousness,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.50,0:17:46.67,Default,,0,0,0,,using the same technique we just did,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.67,0:17:49.79,Default,,0,0,0,,we calibrated all the major motions.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.79,0:17:52.79,Default,,0,0,0,,We have a scale that goes from one to a thousand,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.79,0:17:54.79,Default,,0,0,0,,a logarithmic scale.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.79,0:17:56.79,Default,,0,0,0,,These numbers are 10.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.79,0:17:59.79,Default,,0,0,0,,So this is 10 times 10, 150 times.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.79,0:18:03.79,Default,,0,0,0,,This is 10 times 10, 259, 50 times,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.79,0:18:06.82,Default,,0,0,0,,which is exponential and logarithmic.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.82,0:18:10.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Which is it, logarithmic or exponential?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.36,0:18:12.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Anybody know?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.98,0:18:14.98,Default,,0,0,0,,It's logarithmic exponential.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.98,0:18:16.98,Default,,0,0,0,,It covers it all.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.25,0:18:25.27,Default,,0,0,0,,The highest possible calibration in this planet,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.27,0:18:27.27,Default,,0,0,0,,earthly human life, is a thousand.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.27,0:18:29.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Because that's the way we set up the scale.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.73,0:18:32.73,Default,,0,0,0,,The lowest is death at one.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.73,0:18:35.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Life begins at one and goes up to one thousand.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.73,0:18:38.73,Default,,0,0,0,,We found that anything and everything in this planet
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.73,0:18:40.73,Default,,0,0,0,,could be calibrated.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.73,0:18:43.99,Default,,0,0,0,,And what we discovered we were discovering
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.99,0:18:47.01,Default,,0,0,0,,is how to tell perception from essence.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.01,0:18:51.65,Default,,0,0,0,,How to tell reality from appearance.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.65,0:18:54.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Descartes, the great philosopher.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.65,0:19:00.17,Default,,0,0,0,,The difference between what a thing looks like
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.17,0:19:02.17,Default,,0,0,0,,and what it actually is.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.17,0:19:06.42,Default,,0,0,0,,The wolf in sheep's clothing, how do you discern it?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.42,0:19:09.83,Default,,0,0,0,,And of course, Socrates, my favorite philosopher,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.83,0:19:14.25,Default,,0,0,0,,said, all men chooses only the good.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.25,0:19:17.31,Default,,0,0,0,,That helps you put in place
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.31,0:19:22.07,Default,,0,0,0,,the Christian premise of forgiveness.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.07,0:19:25.07,Default,,0,0,0,,How can you forgive people that seem so?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.07,0:19:28.24,Default,,0,0,0,,When you recall Socrates' teaching,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.24,0:19:32.24,Default,,0,0,0,,all men choose what they think and believe to be the good.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.24,0:19:34.29,Default,,0,0,0,,The only problem is they cannot discern
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.29,0:19:36.29,Default,,0,0,0,,the real good from the false good.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.29,0:19:39.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Therefore, the basic problem is again ignorance,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.29,0:19:42.51,Default,,0,0,0,,not knowing essence from appearance.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.51,0:19:45.45,Default,,0,0,0,,So what we had discovered then,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.45,0:19:48.45,Default,,0,0,0,,with the calibrated levels of consciousness,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.45,0:19:51.45,Default,,0,0,0,,is how to discern essence from appearance
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.45,0:19:54.96,Default,,0,0,0,,for the first time in human history.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.96,0:19:58.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Man goes by appearance and opinion.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.53,0:20:02.53,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, so using the same simple arm technique
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.53,0:20:04.53,Default,,0,0,0,,to hold the thing in mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.53,0:20:07.53,Default,,0,0,0,,So when we calibrate something,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.53,0:20:09.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll just calibrate something.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.53,0:20:11.53,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't have to do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.53,0:20:14.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm holding something in mind now.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.59,0:20:16.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm holding something in mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.59,0:20:17.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I want you to resist.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.59,0:20:19.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Resist.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.69,0:20:22.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm holding something else in mind now.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.69,0:20:23.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I want you to resist.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.69,0:20:27.61,Default,,0,0,0,,The first thing I was holding in mind
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.61,0:20:29.91,Default,,0,0,0,,is a fake,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.91,0:20:33.48,Default,,0,0,0,,a fake,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.48,0:20:35.79,Default,,0,0,0,,a fake Picasso.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.79,0:20:36.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, fake Picasso.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.79,0:20:38.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I just was holding a picture of that.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.79,0:20:40.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Fake Picasso at home.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.90,0:20:44.90,Default,,0,0,0,,And then I also have a couple of legitimate Dali's.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.90,0:20:47.05,Default,,0,0,0,,And I have another painting.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.05,0:20:50.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's see if this is a real one too.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.16,0:20:51.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm holding this one in mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.16,0:20:52.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Resist.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.16,0:20:54.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank God, that's a Miro.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.11,0:21:00.30,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a Miro lithograph.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.30,0:21:02.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Miro died at age 90.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.30,0:21:04.30,Default,,0,0,0,,And suddenly it became very valuable.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.30,0:21:06.30,Default,,0,0,0,,So anyway, I keep it out in the garage
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.30,0:21:10.30,Default,,0,0,0,,so that no harm will come to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.30,0:21:15.16,Default,,0,0,0,,So there's objections to kinesiology
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.16,0:21:17.16,Default,,0,0,0,,and it's the problem of the people
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.16,0:21:18.16,Default,,0,0,0,,who make the objections
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.16,0:21:20.16,Default,,0,0,0,,because you can see
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.16,0:21:22.16,Default,,0,0,0,,even a child can do this.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.16,0:21:23.16,Default,,0,0,0,,And we did a video,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.16,0:21:24.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I think it's called
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.16,0:21:26.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Wall Power versus Force,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.16,0:21:28.16,Default,,0,0,0,,in which we just use a simple child.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.16,0:21:33.54,Default,,0,0,0,,And so it's very simplistic.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.54,0:21:35.54,Default,,0,0,0,,As you can see, it's not suggestive
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.54,0:21:38.54,Default,,0,0,0,,because she doesn't know what I'm holding in mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.54,0:21:41.54,Default,,0,0,0,,The trouble that people ask me sometimes is about dowsing.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.54,0:21:44.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Some super experts can do it with dowsing.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.54,0:21:47.54,Default,,0,0,0,,The trouble with dowsing is the subject and the answer
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.54,0:21:49.54,Default,,0,0,0,,are both the same person.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.54,0:21:52.86,Default,,0,0,0,,The questioner and the answer are the same person.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.86,0:21:53.86,Default,,0,0,0,,And one could have a prejudice,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.86,0:21:54.86,Default,,0,0,0,,in one way or the other,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.86,0:21:56.86,Default,,0,0,0,,that might influence the answer.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.86,0:22:00.16,Default,,0,0,0,,So if it's something really critical,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.16,0:22:02.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't tell her what I'm holding in mind
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.16,0:22:04.16,Default,,0,0,0,,because I don't want the slightest chance
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.16,0:22:06.16,Default,,0,0,0,,of any kind of suggestion taking place.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.16,0:22:07.99,Default,,0,0,0,,To be able to do it,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.99,0:22:10.99,Default,,0,0,0,,you have to be dedicated to truth,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.99,0:22:13.99,Default,,0,0,0,,not to seeking reinforcement
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.99,0:22:16.99,Default,,0,0,0,,of your favorite positionality.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.99,0:22:19.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Understand?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.04,0:22:22.43,Default,,0,0,0,,So it's like a compass.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.43,0:22:24.43,Default,,0,0,0,,The compass then,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.43,0:22:25.43,Default,,0,0,0,,man was without a compass.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.43,0:22:28.43,Default,,0,0,0,,He couldn't tell the truth from falsehood.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.43,0:22:30.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Now he has a compass that's calibrated
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.43,0:22:33.43,Default,,0,0,0,,all the way to a thousand.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.43,0:22:39.88,Default,,0,0,0,,And so we found that everything below level 200 was false.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.88,0:22:43.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Everything above 200 was true.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.06,0:22:48.25,Default,,0,0,0,,And we then incorporated from psychoanalysis
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.25,0:22:51.48,Default,,0,0,0,,also the perennial wisdom,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.48,0:22:54.48,Default,,0,0,0,,also the great chain of being.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.48,0:22:56.48,Default,,0,0,0,,So this is a very familiar
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.48,0:23:00.48,Default,,0,0,0,,listing of levels of consciousness
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.48,0:23:02.48,Default,,0,0,0,,with shame and disgrace
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.48,0:23:04.48,Default,,0,0,0,,and guilt and apathy.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.48,0:23:06.48,Default,,0,0,0,,All the negative ones down here,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.48,0:23:08.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Columbia Psychoanalytic,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.48,0:23:11.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Shandor Rado taught adaptational psychodynamics,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.48,0:23:15.64,Default,,0,0,0,,a variation of Freudian psychoanalysis.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.64,0:23:17.64,Default,,0,0,0,,These recall the emergency emotions.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.64,0:23:20.64,Default,,0,0,0,,These recall the welfare emotions.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.64,0:23:23.64,Default,,0,0,0,,So it also correlates to psychoanalysis.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.64,0:23:26.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I spent four years of psychoanalysis.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.79,0:23:28.89,Default,,0,0,0,,With Lionel Oversee,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.89,0:23:30.89,Default,,0,0,0,,who was a professor at Columbia University,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.89,0:23:33.89,Default,,0,0,0,,whose analyst was Abraham Kardiner,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.89,0:23:35.89,Default,,0,0,0,,whose analyst was Freud.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.89,0:23:37.89,Default,,0,0,0,,So Freud's my great-grandfather.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.55,0:23:43.72,Default,,0,0,0,,He was an atheist.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.48,0:23:50.96,Default,,0,0,0,,My first analyst and I were both atheists.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.96,0:23:53.96,Default,,0,0,0,,We agreed that it was all nonsensical.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.96,0:23:57.81,Default,,0,0,0,,And that lasts you a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.81,0:24:01.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, so here we have all the things
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.43,0:24:04.43,Default,,0,0,0,,that we call the basic feelings.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.43,0:24:06.43,Default,,0,0,0,,And of course we wrote a book called
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.43,0:24:08.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Transcending Levels of Consciousness,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.43,0:24:10.43,Default,,0,0,0,,in which we look at the upside and the downside
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.43,0:24:12.43,Default,,0,0,0,,of what is holding each one of these levels.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.43,0:24:16.23,Default,,0,0,0,,What's holding all negative things in place
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.23,0:24:18.23,Default,,0,0,0,,is one single thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.23,0:24:20.23,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't have to give up anything
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.23,0:24:23.64,Default,,0,0,0,,in this whole world
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.64,0:24:25.99,Default,,0,0,0,,to get off these things here.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.99,0:24:27.99,Default,,0,0,0,,All you have to give up is one thing,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.99,0:24:29.99,Default,,0,0,0,,repeatedly one thing,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:29.99,0:24:32.01,Default,,0,0,0,,no matter what the one thing is.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.01,0:24:33.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Hating your mother-in-law,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:33.01,0:24:35.01,Default,,0,0,0,,feeling guilty about something,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:35.01,0:24:38.33,Default,,0,0,0,,being overcome with greed and lust or what.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:38.33,0:24:40.78,Default,,0,0,0,,The only thing you've got to give up
Dialogue: 0,0:24:40.78,0:24:42.78,Default,,0,0,0,,is the juice that you're getting out of it,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:42.78,0:24:45.78,Default,,0,0,0,,the secret pleasure that you're getting out of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:45.78,0:24:49.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are people so addicted to hatred?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:49.46,0:24:52.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Because they get such wonderful juice out of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:52.46,0:24:54.46,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just so wonderful to get out there
Dialogue: 0,0:24:54.46,0:24:56.46,Default,,0,0,0,,and have a parade and picket and riot
Dialogue: 0,0:24:58.61,0:25:00.61,Default,,0,0,0,,and have a whole hate orgy.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:02.61,0:25:03.61,Default,,0,0,0,,You watch them on TV,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:03.61,0:25:05.61,Default,,0,0,0,,they've got that glee,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:05.61,0:25:07.61,Default,,0,0,0,,it's like an orgy look.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:07.61,0:25:08.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Once you get that look,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:08.61,0:25:10.61,Default,,0,0,0,,you can see it all over the world,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:10.61,0:25:11.61,Default,,0,0,0,,whatever the parade is,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:11.61,0:25:12.61,Default,,0,0,0,,whatever the issue is,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:12.61,0:25:14.61,Default,,0,0,0,,it's all the same look.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:14.61,0:25:16.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm right and you're wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:18.61,0:25:21.76,Default,,0,0,0,,So to get off anything then,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:21.76,0:25:23.76,Default,,0,0,0,,you have to just be willing
Dialogue: 0,0:25:23.76,0:25:25.76,Default,,0,0,0,,to give up whatever juice
Dialogue: 0,0:25:25.76,0:25:27.76,Default,,0,0,0,,you're getting off of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:27.76,0:25:28.76,Default,,0,0,0,,You say,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:28.76,0:25:30.76,Default,,0,0,0,,oh, I'm not getting any juice out of suffering.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:30.76,0:25:33.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh yes, you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:33.31,0:25:35.31,Default,,0,0,0,,You're getting less and less of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:35.31,0:25:37.31,Default,,0,0,0,,You're getting less and less of the juice.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:37.31,0:25:39.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I know people that are still suffering
Dialogue: 0,0:25:39.31,0:25:42.79,Default,,0,0,0,,over the loss of a family member 30 years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:42.79,0:25:46.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't it time to get over it?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:46.40,0:25:48.40,Default,,0,0,0,,No, it's becoming a lifestyle.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:48.40,0:25:49.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Lifestyle.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:49.46,0:25:52.46,Default,,0,0,0,,And the addictiveness that goes with it,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:52.46,0:25:54.58,Default,,0,0,0,,see it every night on television,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:54.58,0:25:56.68,Default,,0,0,0,,you can't get over it.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:56.68,0:25:58.68,Default,,0,0,0,,What was the eagle?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:58.68,0:25:59.68,Default,,0,0,0,,The eagles had a song.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:59.68,0:26:00.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's get over it.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:00.68,0:26:02.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Wasn't that the name of it?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:02.68,0:26:04.68,Default,,0,0,0,,It's time to get over it.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:04.68,0:26:05.68,Default,,0,0,0,,The getting over it
Dialogue: 0,0:26:05.68,0:26:06.68,Default,,0,0,0,,really comes from being willing
Dialogue: 0,0:26:06.68,0:26:09.68,Default,,0,0,0,,to let go the energy
Dialogue: 0,0:26:09.68,0:26:12.68,Default,,0,0,0,,that we get out of the negative positionality.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:12.68,0:26:15.75,Default,,0,0,0,,We finally get up to a level called courage.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:15.75,0:26:18.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Level courage.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:18.79,0:26:20.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Courage is the willingness to tell the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:20.79,0:26:23.79,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the first step in all the 12-step groups.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:23.79,0:26:26.90,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the willingness to take responsibility
Dialogue: 0,0:26:26.90,0:26:28.90,Default,,0,0,0,,and be honest.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:28.90,0:26:31.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Then you move up to neutrality.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:31.11,0:26:34.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Neutrality is a very comfortable place to be.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:34.11,0:26:37.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Neutrality, if you get the job, it's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:37.19,0:26:39.19,Default,,0,0,0,,And if you don't, you'll find another.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:39.19,0:26:41.19,Default,,0,0,0,,So what's the big deal?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:41.19,0:26:43.22,Default,,0,0,0,,We need lots more people
Dialogue: 0,0:26:43.22,0:26:45.22,Default,,0,0,0,,and neutrality in the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:45.22,0:26:48.56,Default,,0,0,0,,People worry about the world ending in the year 2012.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:48.56,0:26:50.56,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the next time the world's supposed to end?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:50.56,0:26:52.56,Default,,0,0,0,,The Mayan calendar?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:52.56,0:26:54.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's take care of the Mayan calendar.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:54.56,0:26:59.72,Default,,0,0,0,,The world is going to end in 2012.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:59.72,0:27:03.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Folks, it's not going to end in 2012.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:03.45,0:27:06.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Those of you who were counting on it,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:06.50,0:27:08.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I hate to disappoint you.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:08.50,0:27:10.67,Default,,0,0,0,,The Mayan calendar has been wrong
Dialogue: 0,0:27:10.67,0:27:11.67,Default,,0,0,0,,for thousands of years,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:11.67,0:27:13.67,Default,,0,0,0,,and it's going to be wrong for thousands of years.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:13.67,0:27:14.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Why is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:14.96,0:27:16.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Because you can't predict the future.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:16.96,0:27:18.96,Default,,0,0,0,,The future is not set.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:18.96,0:27:19.96,Default,,0,0,0,,If the future was set,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:19.96,0:27:22.96,Default,,0,0,0,,there would be no personal responsibility,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:22.96,0:27:24.96,Default,,0,0,0,,no karmic responsibility,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:24.96,0:27:27.96,Default,,0,0,0,,and there would really be no point to evolution itself.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:27.96,0:27:31.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Because this world is optimal
Dialogue: 0,0:27:31.04,0:27:34.04,Default,,0,0,0,,for spiritual evolution.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:34.04,0:27:37.04,Default,,0,0,0,,This world gives you the optimum opportunity
Dialogue: 0,0:27:37.04,0:27:39.04,Default,,0,0,0,,to gain positive karma
Dialogue: 0,0:27:39.04,0:27:41.04,Default,,0,0,0,,and undo negative karma.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:41.04,0:27:44.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Therefore, this world is perfect.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:44.50,0:27:48.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:48.41,0:27:50.41,Default,,0,0,0,,This is a perfect world.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:50.41,0:27:51.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Resist.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:51.41,0:27:57.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Zowie.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:57.96,0:28:01.36,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the essence and appearance.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:01.36,0:28:05.36,Default,,0,0,0,,If God wanted a place where your spirit could evolve,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:05.36,0:28:07.36,Default,,0,0,0,,he would create Earth, wouldn't he?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:07.36,0:28:09.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Every moment you have to make a choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:09.36,0:28:11.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Every single moment you have to make a choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:11.36,0:28:15.63,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't have any choice not to make a choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:15.63,0:28:17.63,Default,,0,0,0,,You always have to make a choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:17.63,0:28:18.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Constantly.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:18.63,0:28:25.97,Default,,0,0,0,,So, the spirit is like a little iron filing
Dialogue: 0,0:28:25.97,0:28:27.97,Default,,0,0,0,,in the infinite field of consciousness,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:27.97,0:28:31.97,Default,,0,0,0,,which is the light of God out of which arose creation.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:31.97,0:28:36.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Therefore, every choice and every decision you make
Dialogue: 0,0:28:36.51,0:28:42.67,Default,,0,0,0,,alters the energy of this little iron filing
Dialogue: 0,0:28:42.67,0:28:45.67,Default,,0,0,0,,that is within this giant electromagnetic field.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:45.67,0:28:48.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Therefore, everything comes about
Dialogue: 0,0:28:48.96,0:28:50.96,Default,,0,0,0,,as a consequence of karmic choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:50.96,0:28:52.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Every time you make a positive choice,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:52.96,0:28:54.96,Default,,0,0,0,,this polarity increases.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:54.96,0:28:56.96,Default,,0,0,0,,A negative choice, a negative polarity.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:56.96,0:29:00.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Therefore, where you are in the overall field
Dialogue: 0,0:29:00.33,0:29:04.33,Default,,0,0,0,,is automatically the consequence of that which you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:04.33,0:29:08.44,Default,,0,0,0,,That which you are is determining what is.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:08.44,0:29:12.46,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no point to worry about Judgment Day
Dialogue: 0,0:29:12.46,0:29:15.03,Default,,0,0,0,,because it's happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:15.03,0:29:20.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Today is Judgment Day.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:20.72,0:29:21.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Resist.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:21.72,0:29:24.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Today and every day is Judgment Day.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:24.88,0:29:26.88,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no point about worrying about
Dialogue: 0,0:29:26.88,0:29:28.88,Default,,0,0,0,,some horrible god in the future
Dialogue: 0,0:29:28.88,0:29:30.88,Default,,0,0,0,,who's going to beat you up,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:30.88,0:29:33.20,Default,,0,0,0,,throw you into hell because he hits you.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:33.20,0:29:36.27,Default,,0,0,0,,You've done it already.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:40.50,0:29:41.96,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:41.96,0:29:44.96,Default,,0,0,0,,So, the justice of God is absolute.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:44.96,0:29:46.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:46.01,0:29:48.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Because it is based on the reality
Dialogue: 0,0:29:48.01,0:29:51.01,Default,,0,0,0,,of that which you have chosen of your own free choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:51.01,0:29:54.04,Default,,0,0,0,,And God's will for us is free choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:54.04,0:29:57.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Free choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:57.07,0:30:00.20,Default,,0,0,0,,To say such things makes me, again,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:00.20,0:30:04.24,Default,,0,0,0,,in the eyes of a relativist, an absolutist.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:04.24,0:30:07.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I might as well have warned everybody here.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:07.24,0:30:09.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I am an absolutist.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:12.65,0:30:15.65,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the absolutism of absolutism
Dialogue: 0,0:30:15.65,0:30:20.59,Default,,0,0,0,,that makes it so absolute.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:20.59,0:30:22.59,Default,,0,0,0,,You chop off a finger, folks.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:22.59,0:30:24.59,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not relative.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:24.59,0:30:27.47,Default,,0,0,0,,It's gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:27.47,0:30:31.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I was going to kick out a relativist
Dialogue: 0,0:30:31.42,0:30:33.71,Default,,0,0,0,,when it comes to money.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:33.71,0:30:35.71,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, these crazy professors and all.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:35.71,0:30:37.71,Default,,0,0,0,,They ridicule everything,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:37.71,0:30:39.71,Default,,0,0,0,,every kind of reality, etc.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:39.71,0:30:41.71,Default,,0,0,0,,When it comes to money, it's amazing
Dialogue: 0,0:30:41.71,0:30:46.75,Default,,0,0,0,,what an absolutist they are.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:46.75,0:30:49.75,Default,,0,0,0,,One man's 50 is another man's 20?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:49.75,0:30:51.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh-uh, that does not go.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:51.75,0:30:54.92,Default,,0,0,0,,One man's 50 is everybody's 50.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:54.92,0:30:57.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Every one of these relativists is an absolutist
Dialogue: 0,0:30:57.92,0:30:59.92,Default,,0,0,0,,when it comes down to the reality
Dialogue: 0,0:30:59.92,0:31:01.92,Default,,0,0,0,,of everyday life.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:01.92,0:31:06.17,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a nice game to play politically, philosophically.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:06.17,0:31:09.17,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, so neutrality, willingness,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:09.17,0:31:12.35,Default,,0,0,0,,in the 300s are very powerful.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:12.35,0:31:16.39,Default,,0,0,0,,The 300s are very powerful.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:16.39,0:31:21.39,Default,,0,0,0,,They build great and do wonderful humanitarian beneficial things.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:21.39,0:31:25.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Rick Warren, what he writes is up there in the high 350s.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:25.39,0:31:27.76,Default,,0,0,0,,You get up to the level of 400s,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:27.76,0:31:30.79,Default,,0,0,0,,you're talking about the intellect,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:30.79,0:31:33.79,Default,,0,0,0,,non-emotional, non-emotional.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:33.79,0:31:35.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Reason and logic.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:35.96,0:31:40.96,Default,,0,0,0,,And then the great scientific geniuses,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:40.96,0:31:45.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Einstein and Freud, etc.,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:45.75,0:31:50.50,Default,,0,0,0,,are at calibration level 499.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:50.50,0:31:54.50,Default,,0,0,0,,499 is as far as you can go with reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:54.50,0:32:00.42,Default,,0,0,0,,The intellect, you can prove what is so.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:00.42,0:32:04.74,Default,,0,0,0,,The differential calculus, 499.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:04.74,0:32:07.74,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, so the reason and the intellect
Dialogue: 0,0:32:07.74,0:32:10.74,Default,,0,0,0,,then is in the range of the mid 400s.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:10.74,0:32:15.25,Default,,0,0,0,,You're still talking about linear reality.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:15.25,0:32:16.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Linear.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:16.25,0:32:18.70,Default,,0,0,0,,That means content.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:18.70,0:32:21.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Now when you get to level 500,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:21.79,0:32:23.79,Default,,0,0,0,,you bring in context.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:23.79,0:32:24.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Context.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:24.79,0:32:27.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Because now you're moving to the non-linear.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:27.79,0:32:31.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Love at 500 is the emergence of the non-linear.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:31.79,0:32:36.81,Default,,0,0,0,,So from 500 up then, we have love,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:36.81,0:32:38.81,Default,,0,0,0,,and then we move on into the higher levels
Dialogue: 0,0:32:38.81,0:32:40.98,Default,,0,0,0,,of selfless love.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:40.98,0:32:43.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Selfless love,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:43.88,0:32:45.88,Default,,0,0,0,,the 12 step groups,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:45.88,0:32:46.88,Default,,0,0,0,,alcoholics and anomalous,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:46.88,0:32:48.88,Default,,0,0,0,,calibrates at 500 and a 40.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:48.88,0:32:51.23,Default,,0,0,0,,500 and a 40.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:51.23,0:32:53.23,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the top few percentage
Dialogue: 0,0:32:53.23,0:32:55.23,Default,,0,0,0,,of all of mankind, 540.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:55.23,0:33:00.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Only 4% of mankind ever gets beyond level 500.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:00.25,0:33:03.25,Default,,0,0,0,,0.4 gets to 540.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:03.25,0:33:06.48,Default,,0,0,0,,People who have recovered in 12 step programs
Dialogue: 0,0:33:06.48,0:33:08.48,Default,,0,0,0,,or A Course in Miracles, etc.,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:08.48,0:33:10.60,Default,,0,0,0,,belong to 0.4.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:10.60,0:33:15.76,Default,,0,0,0,,0.4% of the world's population, statistically.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:15.76,0:33:21.25,Default,,0,0,0,,So 540 is the beginning of a transformation
Dialogue: 0,0:33:21.25,0:33:26.72,Default,,0,0,0,,and it comes about via illumination.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:26.72,0:33:29.72,Default,,0,0,0,,As you get towards level 600,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:29.72,0:33:36.00,Default,,0,0,0,,at about 570 is sainthood.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:36.00,0:33:41.46,Default,,0,0,0,,The Dalai Lama, the Pope, Father Pio.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:41.46,0:33:43.46,Default,,0,0,0,,The level of 570 is
Dialogue: 0,0:33:43.46,0:33:45.68,Default,,0,0,0,,sainthood.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:45.68,0:33:47.91,Default,,0,0,0,,And from 540 and up,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:47.91,0:33:50.91,Default,,0,0,0,,and especially around 570,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:50.91,0:33:53.91,Default,,0,0,0,,there emerges the miraculous.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:53.91,0:33:58.60,Default,,0,0,0,,The miraculous about which mankind goes ooh and ahh.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:58.60,0:34:01.90,Default,,0,0,0,,But in experiential reality,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:01.90,0:34:04.90,Default,,0,0,0,,the miraculous is nothing but the unfolding
Dialogue: 0,0:34:04.90,0:34:06.90,Default,,0,0,0,,of unnatural phenomena.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:06.90,0:34:13.80,Default,,0,0,0,,When you realize that evolution and creation
Dialogue: 0,0:34:13.80,0:34:15.90,Default,,0,0,0,,are one and the same thing,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:15.90,0:34:17.90,Default,,0,0,0,,right now there's so much controversy
Dialogue: 0,0:34:17.90,0:34:25.03,Default,,0,0,0,,about intelligent design versus creationism, etc.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:25.03,0:34:28.03,Default,,0,0,0,,That which shines forth
Dialogue: 0,0:34:28.03,0:34:31.67,Default,,0,0,0,,in the description of Genesis,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:31.67,0:34:33.67,Default,,0,0,0,,the light of God shone forth
Dialogue: 0,0:34:33.67,0:34:38.84,Default,,0,0,0,,out of which arose all of creation.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:38.84,0:34:40.84,Default,,0,0,0,,One thing that arose was
Dialogue: 0,0:34:40.84,0:34:42.84,Default,,0,0,0,,the energy field of life itself.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:42.84,0:34:44.84,Default,,0,0,0,,And so everything that we calibrate
Dialogue: 0,0:34:44.84,0:34:48.84,Default,,0,0,0,,is in comparison to an infinite field of consciousness.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:48.84,0:34:51.84,Default,,0,0,0,,The infinite field called consciousness,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:51.84,0:34:55.03,Default,,0,0,0,,which is beyond time and place,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:55.03,0:34:57.03,Default,,0,0,0,,beyond time and place,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:57.03,0:34:59.03,Default,,0,0,0,,has no beginning and no ending.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:59.03,0:35:01.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Therefore it's impossible
Dialogue: 0,0:35:01.42,0:35:03.42,Default,,0,0,0,,to prove the existence of God
Dialogue: 0,0:35:03.42,0:35:06.42,Default,,0,0,0,,because that which is infinite,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:06.42,0:35:08.42,Default,,0,0,0,,limitless, has no beginning and ending,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:08.42,0:35:12.46,Default,,0,0,0,,is in a different paradigm of reality than proof.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:12.46,0:35:15.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Proof is the world of the 400s.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:15.75,0:35:18.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Spiritual reality starts at 500 and up.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:18.88,0:35:20.88,Default,,0,0,0,,It has to do with essence.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:20.88,0:35:28.73,Default,,0,0,0,,It has to do with radical subjectivity.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:28.73,0:35:32.03,Default,,0,0,0,,The reason certain things became apparent
Dialogue: 0,0:35:32.03,0:35:37.03,Default,,0,0,0,,was because when I saw kinesiology demonstrated,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:37.03,0:35:41.19,Default,,0,0,0,,they presumed that it was a local phenomena
Dialogue: 0,0:35:41.19,0:35:43.19,Default,,0,0,0,,based on the Newtonian premise of causality.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:43.19,0:35:46.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Causality applies to the energy fields
Dialogue: 0,0:35:46.19,0:35:52.11,Default,,0,0,0,,of the 400s science.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:52.11,0:35:54.11,Default,,0,0,0,,But the way things come about
Dialogue: 0,0:35:54.11,0:35:56.11,Default,,0,0,0,,is not via causality.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:56.11,0:35:57.11,Default,,0,0,0,,That is a mentalization
Dialogue: 0,0:35:57.11,0:35:59.11,Default,,0,0,0,,that you project into the world
Dialogue: 0,0:35:59.11,0:36:01.11,Default,,0,0,0,,like you do with time.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:01.11,0:36:02.11,Default,,0,0,0,,There is no time out there.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:02.11,0:36:03.11,Default,,0,0,0,,There is no space.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:03.11,0:36:04.11,Default,,0,0,0,,There is no distance.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:04.11,0:36:06.11,Default,,0,0,0,,There is no causality.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:06.11,0:36:10.69,Default,,0,0,0,,And there is no before or after.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:10.69,0:36:12.69,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the way it looks to your witnessing.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:12.69,0:36:14.69,Default,,0,0,0,,The fact that you witness things progressively
Dialogue: 0,0:36:14.69,0:36:17.69,Default,,0,0,0,,doesn't mean that they are that way in the universe.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:17.69,0:36:19.69,Default,,0,0,0,,You see the grandiosity of the ego.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:19.69,0:36:20.69,Default,,0,0,0,,If I see it that way,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:20.69,0:36:24.19,Default,,0,0,0,,that's the way it must be in the universe.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:24.19,0:36:26.19,Default,,0,0,0,,The universe has no interest
Dialogue: 0,0:36:26.19,0:36:29.19,Default,,0,0,0,,in the sequence in which you're witnessing here.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:29.19,0:36:32.65,Default,,0,0,0,,So what you're actually watching
Dialogue: 0,0:36:32.65,0:36:34.65,Default,,0,0,0,,is that everything is occurring
Dialogue: 0,0:36:34.65,0:36:37.65,Default,,0,0,0,,of its own spontaneously
Dialogue: 0,0:36:37.65,0:36:41.75,Default,,0,0,0,,as the phenomena of emergence,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:41.75,0:36:45.07,Default,,0,0,0,,potentiality becoming an actuality.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:45.07,0:36:48.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Things do not happen by causality.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:48.42,0:36:50.42,Default,,0,0,0,,That's an impossibility
Dialogue: 0,0:36:50.42,0:36:54.96,Default,,0,0,0,,because you end up in an infinite progressive series.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:54.96,0:37:04.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Everything that happens is happening spontaneously.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:04.48,0:37:07.69,Default,,0,0,0,,There isn't even any personal you
Dialogue: 0,0:37:07.69,0:37:08.69,Default,,0,0,0,,making it happen,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:08.69,0:37:10.69,Default,,0,0,0,,although you think there is.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:10.69,0:37:14.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Duality arises from thinking
Dialogue: 0,0:37:14.53,0:37:17.53,Default,,0,0,0,,that there is a separate personal you
Dialogue: 0,0:37:17.53,0:37:22.55,Default,,0,0,0,,that is the originator of all action,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:22.55,0:37:24.55,Default,,0,0,0,,the motivator, the decider.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:24.55,0:37:29.28,Default,,0,0,0,,In reality, everything is happening spontaneously.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:29.28,0:37:33.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Potentiality, when local conditions are right,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:33.28,0:37:36.28,Default,,0,0,0,,emerges into an actuality.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:36.28,0:37:39.51,Default,,0,0,0,,And that's the same phenomena
Dialogue: 0,0:37:39.51,0:37:41.51,Default,,0,0,0,,we see within the miraculous.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:41.51,0:37:43.51,Default,,0,0,0,,The miraculous is nothing but
Dialogue: 0,0:37:43.51,0:37:45.67,Default,,0,0,0,,the potentiation,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:45.67,0:37:47.67,Default,,0,0,0,,the activation of that potentiation
Dialogue: 0,0:37:47.67,0:37:49.67,Default,,0,0,0,,into an actuality
Dialogue: 0,0:37:49.67,0:37:53.00,Default,,0,0,0,,by virtue of the field of the context.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:53.00,0:37:56.00,Default,,0,0,0,,The higher the spiritual energy of the context,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:56.00,0:37:58.00,Default,,0,0,0,,the greater the likelihood
Dialogue: 0,0:37:58.00,0:38:01.25,Default,,0,0,0,,that what is held in mind will potentiate.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:01.25,0:38:03.25,Default,,0,0,0,,At a certain level of consciousness,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:03.25,0:38:05.25,Default,,0,0,0,,the witnessing of life
Dialogue: 0,0:38:05.25,0:38:06.25,Default,,0,0,0,,is once
Dialogue: 0,0:38:06.25,0:38:10.82,Default,,0,0,0,,one continuous miracle after another.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:10.82,0:38:13.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Everything is happening of its own
Dialogue: 0,0:38:13.86,0:38:17.30,Default,,0,0,0,,by virtue of that which it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:17.30,0:38:21.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:21.88,0:38:22.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know what all that meant,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:22.88,0:38:24.88,Default,,0,0,0,,but it certainly sounded good, didn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:24.88,0:38:35.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I know what it means.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:35.21,0:38:44.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe we should go to the next slide.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:44.26,0:38:46.26,Default,,0,0,0,,In this lifetime,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:46.26,0:38:48.32,Default,,0,0,0,,the reason I recognize
Dialogue: 0,0:38:48.32,0:38:50.32,Default,,0,0,0,,what's going on with kinesiology
Dialogue: 0,0:38:50.32,0:38:52.32,Default,,0,0,0,,is because I've had rather astonishing
Dialogue: 0,0:38:52.32,0:38:54.32,Default,,0,0,0,,spiritual experiences throughout life,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:54.32,0:38:56.32,Default,,0,0,0,,starting at a very young age.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:56.32,0:38:58.67,Default,,0,0,0,,People like me didn't talk about it,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:58.67,0:38:59.67,Default,,0,0,0,,so I give it a few minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:59.67,0:39:02.03,Default,,0,0,0,,The rest of it's in the book.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:02.03,0:39:03.03,Default,,0,0,0,,It began at age three,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:03.03,0:39:05.03,Default,,0,0,0,,when out of nothingness,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:05.03,0:39:08.48,Default,,0,0,0,,there came the sudden shock of existence,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:08.48,0:39:10.67,Default,,0,0,0,,out of oblivion,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:10.67,0:39:13.65,Default,,0,0,0,,out of the void,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:13.65,0:39:15.65,Default,,0,0,0,,where I went from previous lifetimes
Dialogue: 0,0:39:15.65,0:39:18.19,Default,,0,0,0,,as a Hinayana Buddhist
Dialogue: 0,0:39:18.19,0:39:20.19,Default,,0,0,0,,into the void.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:20.19,0:39:23.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I would leave that lifetime in the void.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:23.19,0:39:25.48,Default,,0,0,0,,This lifetime, at age three,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:25.48,0:39:26.48,Default,,0,0,0,,suddenly,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:26.48,0:39:28.48,Default,,0,0,0,,there was a shock.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:28.48,0:39:31.48,Default,,0,0,0,,It was like suddenly turned on the Klee lights,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:31.48,0:39:33.71,Default,,0,0,0,,and I realized that I existed.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:33.71,0:39:38.05,Default,,0,0,0,,It was a stunning, terrible shock.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:38.05,0:39:40.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I was not happy about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:40.86,0:39:42.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I was not pleased to exist.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:42.86,0:39:44.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Not only was it bad enough to exist,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:44.88,0:39:46.88,Default,,0,0,0,,but with it went this little body.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:46.88,0:39:49.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Ha!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:49.17,0:39:51.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Three-year-old body in a wagon.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:51.65,0:39:52.65,Default,,0,0,0,,First, you exist.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:52.65,0:39:53.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Secondly, you got this body with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:53.65,0:39:56.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, my God.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:56.26,0:39:57.26,Default,,0,0,0,,The next thing that arose,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:57.26,0:39:58.26,Default,,0,0,0,,this is all nonverbal,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:58.26,0:39:59.26,Default,,0,0,0,,the next thing that arose
Dialogue: 0,0:39:59.26,0:40:02.26,Default,,0,0,0,,was suddenly the fear of nonexistence.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:02.26,0:40:05.26,Default,,0,0,0,,If I had come into existence,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:05.26,0:40:07.26,Default,,0,0,0,,then it could have arisen
Dialogue: 0,0:40:07.26,0:40:11.26,Default,,0,0,0,,that I would not have come into existence,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:11.26,0:40:16.36,Default,,0,0,0,,which was just a total awareness.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:16.36,0:40:18.36,Default,,0,0,0,,So, there arose the conundrum,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:18.36,0:40:22.38,Default,,0,0,0,,which this life was about for many years.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:22.38,0:40:25.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Was reality existence or nonexistence?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:25.38,0:40:30.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Was reality beyond existence or nonexistence,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:30.51,0:40:31.51,Default,,0,0,0,,which can't be solved
Dialogue: 0,0:40:31.51,0:40:34.51,Default,,0,0,0,,if you go past consciousness level 850.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:34.51,0:40:37.69,Default,,0,0,0,,So, I came in as nothingness,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:37.69,0:40:39.69,Default,,0,0,0,,nothingness was the absolute reality,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:39.69,0:40:41.96,Default,,0,0,0,,nothingness.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:41.96,0:40:45.40,Default,,0,0,0,,From there, a lot of rather profound
Dialogue: 0,0:40:45.40,0:40:47.40,Default,,0,0,0,,spiritual experiences happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:47.40,0:40:49.40,Default,,0,0,0,,They were all spontaneous,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:49.40,0:40:52.40,Default,,0,0,0,,in which I experienced
Dialogue: 0,0:40:52.40,0:40:55.53,Default,,0,0,0,,the infinite radiance of the self,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:55.53,0:40:59.59,Default,,0,0,0,,and whether the physical body
Dialogue: 0,0:40:59.59,0:41:01.59,Default,,0,0,0,,continued to exist or not
Dialogue: 0,0:41:01.59,0:41:03.88,Default,,0,0,0,,was totally irrelevant,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:03.88,0:41:05.88,Default,,0,0,0,,because in that state,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:05.88,0:41:07.88,Default,,0,0,0,,it's timeless.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:07.88,0:41:09.88,Default,,0,0,0,,So, in a snowbank somewhere
Dialogue: 0,0:41:09.88,0:41:12.26,Default,,0,0,0,,in the highways of Wisconsin,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:12.26,0:41:15.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I climbed in and out of this blizzard
Dialogue: 0,0:41:15.57,0:41:18.57,Default,,0,0,0,,and this incredible blissful condition
Dialogue: 0,0:41:18.57,0:41:20.57,Default,,0,0,0,,overwhelmed,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:20.57,0:41:23.57,Default,,0,0,0,,and there was no personal self anymore,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:23.57,0:41:25.57,Default,,0,0,0,,just an infinite presence
Dialogue: 0,0:41:25.57,0:41:27.92,Default,,0,0,0,,beyond all description,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:27.92,0:41:29.92,Default,,0,0,0,,beyond all time,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:29.92,0:41:34.48,Default,,0,0,0,,with no beginning and no end.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:34.48,0:41:39.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Its characteristics were power,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:39.23,0:41:41.23,Default,,0,0,0,,power beyond all description.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:41.23,0:41:45.44,Default,,0,0,0,,The power of divine love is invincible.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:45.44,0:41:50.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Its invincibility is based on the fact
Dialogue: 0,0:41:50.00,0:41:52.00,Default,,0,0,0,,that it is absolute.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:52.00,0:41:55.21,Default,,0,0,0,,The absolute power of divinity
Dialogue: 0,0:41:55.21,0:41:57.21,Default,,0,0,0,,is an absolute,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:57.21,0:42:02.92,Default,,0,0,0,,and simultaneously exquisitely soft,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:02.92,0:42:06.36,Default,,0,0,0,,so that what was left of the self,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:06.36,0:42:07.36,Default,,0,0,0,,personal self,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:07.36,0:42:08.36,Default,,0,0,0,,melts,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:08.36,0:42:11.36,Default,,0,0,0,,melted into this infinite beingness.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:11.36,0:42:14.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Then came the knowingness,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:14.51,0:42:15.51,Default,,0,0,0,,the reality,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:15.51,0:42:18.23,Default,,0,0,0,,that that which I am
Dialogue: 0,0:42:18.23,0:42:20.23,Default,,0,0,0,,existed before all time.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:20.23,0:42:22.90,Default,,0,0,0,,That which I am
Dialogue: 0,0:42:22.90,0:42:26.90,Default,,0,0,0,,will exist beyond all universes,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:26.90,0:42:29.90,Default,,0,0,0,,after all universes have disappeared,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:29.90,0:42:32.01,Default,,0,0,0,,resist.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:32.01,0:42:34.84,Default,,0,0,0,,An absolute knowingness.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:34.84,0:42:39.48,Default,,0,0,0,,The thing about spiritual reality
Dialogue: 0,0:42:39.48,0:42:42.09,Default,,0,0,0,,is that it is an absolute,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:42.09,0:42:45.15,Default,,0,0,0,,experientially,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:45.15,0:42:46.15,Default,,0,0,0,,experientially,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:46.15,0:42:48.34,Default,,0,0,0,,it is an absolute.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:48.34,0:42:49.34,Default,,0,0,0,,It's non-verbal,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:49.34,0:42:51.34,Default,,0,0,0,,no questions can be asked,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:51.34,0:42:52.34,Default,,0,0,0,,none arise,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:52.34,0:42:54.34,Default,,0,0,0,,because they have all been answered.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:54.34,0:42:58.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Because of such experiences
Dialogue: 0,0:42:58.23,0:43:00.23,Default,,0,0,0,,when I saw kinesiology,
Dialogue: 0,0:43:00.23,0:43:03.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I saw that it was not a Newtonian causal,
Dialogue: 0,0:43:03.23,0:43:05.23,Default,,0,0,0,,cause and effect kind of relationship.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:05.23,0:43:07.32,Default,,0,0,0,,What I saw was that
Dialogue: 0,0:43:07.32,0:43:11.42,Default,,0,0,0,,what the person was responding to
Dialogue: 0,0:43:11.42,0:43:14.42,Default,,0,0,0,,was the energy field of consciousness itself,
Dialogue: 0,0:43:14.42,0:43:18.51,Default,,0,0,0,,it's not a linear causality.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:18.51,0:43:21.44,Default,,0,0,0,,When I hold in mind something
Dialogue: 0,0:43:21.44,0:43:23.44,Default,,0,0,0,,and press down her arm,
Dialogue: 0,0:43:23.44,0:43:25.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm holding the energy field
Dialogue: 0,0:43:25.76,0:43:27.76,Default,,0,0,0,,of the essence of that,
Dialogue: 0,0:43:27.76,0:43:30.55,Default,,0,0,0,,and what her arm is responding to
Dialogue: 0,0:43:30.55,0:43:32.55,Default,,0,0,0,,is the essence.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:32.55,0:43:34.71,Default,,0,0,0,,If the essence is over 200,
Dialogue: 0,0:43:34.71,0:43:35.71,Default,,0,0,0,,she stays strong.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:35.71,0:43:37.71,Default,,0,0,0,,If the essence is under 200,
Dialogue: 0,0:43:37.71,0:43:38.71,Default,,0,0,0,,she goes weak.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:38.71,0:43:39.98,Default,,0,0,0,,She doesn't even know
Dialogue: 0,0:43:39.98,0:43:41.98,Default,,0,0,0,,why I'm holding in mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:41.98,0:43:44.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Everybody got that?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:44.11,0:43:46.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to get that very well.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:46.11,0:43:48.11,Default,,0,0,0,,It's non-linear.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:48.11,0:43:50.11,Default,,0,0,0,,It has nothing to do with reason,
Dialogue: 0,0:43:50.11,0:43:52.11,Default,,0,0,0,,argument, logic, etc.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:52.11,0:43:54.30,Default,,0,0,0,,So all comes about then
Dialogue: 0,0:43:54.30,0:43:57.30,Default,,0,0,0,,as a virtue of that which it is,
Dialogue: 0,0:43:57.30,0:43:59.48,Default,,0,0,0,,potentiality,
Dialogue: 0,0:43:59.48,0:44:02.67,Default,,0,0,0,,which is actualized by the field.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:02.67,0:44:05.78,Default,,0,0,0,,So the field is what actualizes
Dialogue: 0,0:44:05.78,0:44:07.78,Default,,0,0,0,,the kinesiologic response.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:07.78,0:44:10.78,Default,,0,0,0,,It's also the field that actualizes
Dialogue: 0,0:44:10.78,0:44:12.78,Default,,0,0,0,,what the world calls the miraculous
Dialogue: 0,0:44:12.78,0:44:14.78,Default,,0,0,0,,from energy field.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:14.78,0:44:16.80,Default,,0,0,0,,540,
Dialogue: 0,0:44:16.80,0:44:20.63,Default,,0,0,0,,the miraculous is common
Dialogue: 0,0:44:20.63,0:44:22.90,Default,,0,0,0,,in 12-step groups,
Dialogue: 0,0:44:22.90,0:44:25.15,Default,,0,0,0,,and Course in Miracles, of course,
Dialogue: 0,0:44:25.15,0:44:26.15,Default,,0,0,0,,is based on that.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:26.15,0:44:28.15,Default,,0,0,0,,570 and up,
Dialogue: 0,0:44:28.15,0:44:31.15,Default,,0,0,0,,the miraculous is almost continuous.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:31.15,0:44:33.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Everything is just in place
Dialogue: 0,0:44:33.15,0:44:35.15,Default,,0,0,0,,the way it's supposed to be,
Dialogue: 0,0:44:35.15,0:44:37.15,Default,,0,0,0,,and everything is perfect.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:37.15,0:44:39.15,Default,,0,0,0,,And so the world doesn't go
Dialogue: 0,0:44:39.15,0:44:41.15,Default,,0,0,0,,from imperfection to perfection.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:41.15,0:44:43.48,Default,,0,0,0,,The world in reality,
Dialogue: 0,0:44:43.48,0:44:45.48,Default,,0,0,0,,when you really see it for what it is,
Dialogue: 0,0:44:45.48,0:44:47.48,Default,,0,0,0,,goes from perfection to perfection.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:47.48,0:44:53.28,Default,,0,0,0,,As a spiritual discipline then,
Dialogue: 0,0:44:53.28,0:44:55.28,Default,,0,0,0,,you make a decision
Dialogue: 0,0:44:55.28,0:44:57.28,Default,,0,0,0,,to see the intrinsic beauty and perfection
Dialogue: 0,0:44:57.28,0:44:59.28,Default,,0,0,0,,of all that exists no matter what.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:59.28,0:45:01.90,Default,,0,0,0,,The mind will make objections.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:01.90,0:45:03.90,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't mean that garbage can
Dialogue: 0,0:45:03.90,0:45:06.34,Default,,0,0,0,,laying over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:06.34,0:45:08.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, I mean that garbage can
Dialogue: 0,0:45:08.34,0:45:11.15,Default,,0,0,0,,laying over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:11.15,0:45:13.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I remember walking down an alley
Dialogue: 0,0:45:13.15,0:45:14.15,Default,,0,0,0,,in New York City,
Dialogue: 0,0:45:14.15,0:45:16.15,Default,,0,0,0,,and here's two old beautiful garbage cans
Dialogue: 0,0:45:16.15,0:45:18.36,Default,,0,0,0,,and a couple of mice running around,
Dialogue: 0,0:45:18.36,0:45:21.53,Default,,0,0,0,,and I merged into that awareness.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:21.53,0:45:23.53,Default,,0,0,0,,It was like an incredible painting.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:23.53,0:45:25.53,Default,,0,0,0,,It was like an impressionistic painting.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:25.53,0:45:27.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Here's these garbage cans like this,
Dialogue: 0,0:45:27.53,0:45:29.53,Default,,0,0,0,,and little mice like this running all over,
Dialogue: 0,0:45:29.53,0:45:31.53,Default,,0,0,0,,and everything is all collapsed like that,
Dialogue: 0,0:45:31.53,0:45:33.53,Default,,0,0,0,,and the tin can is laying there,
Dialogue: 0,0:45:33.53,0:45:35.53,Default,,0,0,0,,and it's just a stunning,
Dialogue: 0,0:45:35.53,0:45:37.53,Default,,0,0,0,,what do you call it,
Dialogue: 0,0:45:37.53,0:45:40.19,Default,,0,0,0,,montage or whatever the word is in art.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:40.19,0:45:42.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Within everything then is,
Dialogue: 0,0:45:42.19,0:45:44.19,Default,,0,0,0,,because of its perfection,
Dialogue: 0,0:45:44.19,0:45:47.44,Default,,0,0,0,,everything goes from perfection
Dialogue: 0,0:45:47.44,0:45:49.44,Default,,0,0,0,,to perfection.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:49.44,0:45:51.44,Default,,0,0,0,,And so,
Dialogue: 0,0:45:51.44,0:45:53.44,Default,,0,0,0,,everything goes from perfection
Dialogue: 0,0:45:53.44,0:45:55.61,Default,,0,0,0,,to perfection.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:55.61,0:45:57.61,Default,,0,0,0,,You say, well what about this half-grown rose?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:57.61,0:45:59.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it an imperfect rose?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:59.61,0:46:01.61,Default,,0,0,0,,No,
Dialogue: 0,0:46:01.61,0:46:03.61,Default,,0,0,0,,it's a perfectly half-grown rose.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:03.61,0:46:05.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Understand?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:05.61,0:46:07.61,Default,,0,0,0,,It can only move from perfection
Dialogue: 0,0:46:07.61,0:46:09.67,Default,,0,0,0,,to perfection.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:09.67,0:46:11.67,Default,,0,0,0,,This is a perfect half-grown rose.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:11.67,0:46:13.71,Default,,0,0,0,,This is a perfect three-quarters.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:13.71,0:46:15.71,Default,,0,0,0,,This is a perfect full.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:15.71,0:46:17.71,Default,,0,0,0,,This is a perfect faded rose.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:17.71,0:46:19.71,Default,,0,0,0,,This is a perfect dyed,
Dialogue: 0,0:46:19.71,0:46:21.73,Default,,0,0,0,,dried up,
Dialogue: 0,0:46:21.73,0:46:23.73,Default,,0,0,0,,old,
Dialogue: 0,0:46:23.73,0:46:27.88,Default,,0,0,0,,crossing rose.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:27.88,0:46:29.88,Default,,0,0,0,,It goes from perfectly almost
Dialogue: 0,0:46:29.88,0:46:31.88,Default,,0,0,0,,to perfectly full,
Dialogue: 0,0:46:31.88,0:46:33.88,Default,,0,0,0,,to perfectly faded,
Dialogue: 0,0:46:33.88,0:46:35.88,Default,,0,0,0,,to perfectly dried up,
Dialogue: 0,0:46:35.88,0:46:39.07,Default,,0,0,0,,and then it blows away into perfect dust.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:39.07,0:46:41.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you see its perfection at every second?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:41.07,0:46:43.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Everything is that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:46.38,0:46:50.01,Default,,0,0,0,,What the world, what you think is destruction
Dialogue: 0,0:46:50.01,0:46:52.01,Default,,0,0,0,,is the perfection of the
Dialogue: 0,0:46:52.01,0:46:54.48,Default,,0,0,0,,emergence of that potentiality.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:54.48,0:46:57.80,Default,,0,0,0,,As the ship goes over,
Dialogue: 0,0:46:57.80,0:46:59.80,Default,,0,0,0,,they all drown
Dialogue: 0,0:46:59.80,0:47:03.15,Default,,0,0,0,,at the same time.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:03.15,0:47:08.98,Default,,0,0,0,,La la.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:08.98,0:47:10.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Wasn't that a great drowning we did
Dialogue: 0,0:47:10.98,0:47:12.98,Default,,0,0,0,,when they came down the other side?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:12.98,0:47:17.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Man, that really turned on the TV and everybody.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:17.55,0:47:19.55,Default,,0,0,0,,People go out with a dramatic bang,
Dialogue: 0,0:47:19.55,0:47:21.55,Default,,0,0,0,,don't they?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:21.55,0:47:23.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Look at the lengths that people go through
Dialogue: 0,0:47:23.55,0:47:26.59,Default,,0,0,0,,to get out of here, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:26.59,0:47:28.59,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't just simply quietly slump over.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:28.59,0:47:30.59,Default,,0,0,0,,You gotta do a whole big deal out of it,
Dialogue: 0,0:47:30.59,0:47:32.59,Default,,0,0,0,,drive off a cliff, have the police there,
Dialogue: 0,0:47:32.59,0:47:34.69,Default,,0,0,0,,9-11, God all help us.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:34.69,0:47:38.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright, so let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:38.48,0:47:40.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Everything then is the perfect
Dialogue: 0,0:47:40.48,0:47:42.48,Default,,0,0,0,,fulfillment of potential. Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:42.48,0:47:44.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Because this world is
Dialogue: 0,0:47:44.48,0:47:46.48,Default,,0,0,0,,perfect for the undoing of negative
Dialogue: 0,0:47:46.48,0:47:48.48,Default,,0,0,0,,karma and the gaining of positive
Dialogue: 0,0:47:48.48,0:47:50.48,Default,,0,0,0,,karma. This world is
Dialogue: 0,0:47:50.48,0:47:52.71,Default,,0,0,0,,maximal. Let's see if
Dialogue: 0,0:47:52.71,0:47:56.40,Default,,0,0,0,,that's so. We have permission
Dialogue: 0,0:47:56.40,0:47:58.44,Default,,0,0,0,,to ask that. That is so.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:58.44,0:48:00.44,Default,,0,0,0,,What the Buddha said is truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:00.44,0:48:02.44,Default,,0,0,0,,The Buddha wasn't lying, folks.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:04.63,0:48:07.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I told him, I said,
Dialogue: 0,0:48:07.11,0:48:09.11,Default,,0,0,0,,when I get back there, I want to remind everybody
Dialogue: 0,0:48:09.11,0:48:11.11,Default,,0,0,0,,that you were telling the truth, in case they'd forgotten.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:14.17,0:48:16.26,Default,,0,0,0,,They think the Buddha
Dialogue: 0,0:48:16.26,0:48:18.26,Default,,0,0,0,,only applies to the Eastern world.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:18.26,0:48:23.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, okay, right.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:23.36,0:48:25.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Infinite potentiality, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:25.36,0:48:29.32,Default,,0,0,0,,These are the scale of the
Dialogue: 0,0:48:29.32,0:48:31.51,Default,,0,0,0,,enlightened states.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:31.51,0:48:34.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know where
Dialogue: 0,0:48:34.38,0:48:36.38,Default,,0,0,0,,the calibrations are. They all calibrate
Dialogue: 0,0:48:36.38,0:48:39.76,Default,,0,0,0,,a thousand and over.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:39.76,0:48:41.78,Default,,0,0,0,,If you ask
Dialogue: 0,0:48:41.78,0:48:43.78,Default,,0,0,0,,the arm what these are, these are all
Dialogue: 0,0:48:43.78,0:48:45.78,Default,,0,0,0,,infinite.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:45.78,0:48:47.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:47.94,0:48:49.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Then you leave this
Dialogue: 0,0:48:49.94,0:48:52.13,Default,,0,0,0,,experiential universe,
Dialogue: 0,0:48:52.13,0:48:54.13,Default,,0,0,0,,and you get to angels and archangels.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:54.13,0:48:56.61,Default,,0,0,0,,And
Dialogue: 0,0:48:56.61,0:48:58.61,Default,,0,0,0,,my own salvation came about
Dialogue: 0,0:48:58.61,0:49:01.03,Default,,0,0,0,,in this lifetime.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:01.03,0:49:04.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Out of the pits of hell,
Dialogue: 0,0:49:04.67,0:49:06.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I would not advise anybody
Dialogue: 0,0:49:06.67,0:49:08.67,Default,,0,0,0,,to take any risk of going to hell
Dialogue: 0,0:49:08.67,0:49:12.65,Default,,0,0,0,,under any circumstances.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:12.65,0:49:15.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me be a witness.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:15.57,0:49:17.57,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't want to take any chances at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:17.57,0:49:19.57,Default,,0,0,0,,You just do not want to even
Dialogue: 0,0:49:19.57,0:49:21.84,Default,,0,0,0,,give it a thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:21.84,0:49:23.84,Default,,0,0,0,,To risk hell, see.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:23.84,0:49:25.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Because there are levels of hell
Dialogue: 0,0:49:25.90,0:49:27.90,Default,,0,0,0,,far deeper than even Dante
Dialogue: 0,0:49:27.90,0:49:29.90,Default,,0,0,0,,realized.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:29.90,0:49:31.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Dante was extremely correct.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:31.90,0:49:33.90,Default,,0,0,0,,The upper levels of hell.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:33.90,0:49:36.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Because when I hit the pits of hell,
Dialogue: 0,0:49:36.40,0:49:38.40,Default,,0,0,0,,through inner spiritual exploration
Dialogue: 0,0:49:38.40,0:49:40.40,Default,,0,0,0,,and despair,
Dialogue: 0,0:49:40.40,0:49:42.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I was an atheist at the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:42.96,0:49:44.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I was a religionist
Dialogue: 0,0:49:44.96,0:49:46.96,Default,,0,0,0,,all my life.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:46.96,0:49:48.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Brought up in a very religious
Dialogue: 0,0:49:48.96,0:49:51.15,Default,,0,0,0,,environment.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:51.15,0:49:53.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I was an acolyte.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:53.15,0:49:55.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I sang in the choir.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:55.55,0:49:58.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I was a boy soprano, sort of.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:58.03,0:50:00.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I sang in the Great Lakes in the old choir.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:00.03,0:50:02.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Eventually, I became an atheist
Dialogue: 0,0:50:02.11,0:50:04.11,Default,,0,0,0,,for the reason that,
Dialogue: 0,0:50:04.11,0:50:06.13,Default,,0,0,0,,how can anybody so religious be an atheist?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:06.13,0:50:08.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I was walking through the woods one day
Dialogue: 0,0:50:08.13,0:50:10.84,Default,,0,0,0,,thinking of nothing at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:10.84,0:50:13.36,Default,,0,0,0,,And all of a sudden,
Dialogue: 0,0:50:13.36,0:50:15.36,Default,,0,0,0,,all the great things that have happened to me
Dialogue: 0,0:50:15.36,0:50:17.36,Default,,0,0,0,,came as a revelation.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:17.36,0:50:19.61,Default,,0,0,0,,This was not such a great thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:19.61,0:50:21.61,Default,,0,0,0,,This was the opposite.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:21.61,0:50:24.73,Default,,0,0,0,,All of a sudden, out of nothingness,
Dialogue: 0,0:50:24.73,0:50:26.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I grasped the totality
Dialogue: 0,0:50:26.73,0:50:28.73,Default,,0,0,0,,of the suffering
Dialogue: 0,0:50:28.73,0:50:31.07,Default,,0,0,0,,of mankind
Dialogue: 0,0:50:31.07,0:50:34.71,Default,,0,0,0,,throughout all of time.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:34.71,0:50:36.71,Default,,0,0,0,,The totality of the suffering
Dialogue: 0,0:50:36.71,0:50:38.71,Default,,0,0,0,,of all of mankind
Dialogue: 0,0:50:38.71,0:50:42.28,Default,,0,0,0,,throughout all of time.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:42.28,0:50:44.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I was staggered.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:44.28,0:50:48.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I was staggered.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:48.07,0:50:50.26,Default,,0,0,0,,In that moment, I became an atheist.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:50.26,0:50:53.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I said, any god that could allow
Dialogue: 0,0:50:53.57,0:50:56.48,Default,,0,0,0,,what I comprehended,
Dialogue: 0,0:50:56.48,0:50:59.69,Default,,0,0,0,,there couldn't be a god.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:59.69,0:51:01.69,Default,,0,0,0,,And I became
Dialogue: 0,0:51:01.69,0:51:03.69,Default,,0,0,0,,an intense atheist,
Dialogue: 0,0:51:03.69,0:51:08.40,Default,,0,0,0,,not an amateur.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:08.40,0:51:10.40,Default,,0,0,0,,In order to be something,
Dialogue: 0,0:51:10.40,0:51:12.40,Default,,0,0,0,,you better become an expert
Dialogue: 0,0:51:12.40,0:51:14.40,Default,,0,0,0,,at what you're going to be.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:14.40,0:51:16.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Catholic theology, et cetera.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:16.53,0:51:18.53,Default,,0,0,0,,So I knew what my enemy was.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:18.53,0:51:20.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I could ridicule
Dialogue: 0,0:51:20.57,0:51:22.57,Default,,0,0,0,,the reasons that prove
Dialogue: 0,0:51:22.57,0:51:25.44,Default,,0,0,0,,the existence of God from
Dialogue: 0,0:51:25.44,0:51:27.44,Default,,0,0,0,,first cause.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:27.44,0:51:29.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Give me a break, first cause.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:29.44,0:51:31.59,Default,,0,0,0,,It still gives me a laugh.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:31.59,0:51:35.51,Default,,0,0,0,,That which is eternal
Dialogue: 0,0:51:35.51,0:51:37.51,Default,,0,0,0,,couldn't possibly have a cause,
Dialogue: 0,0:51:37.51,0:51:39.51,Default,,0,0,0,,much less a first cause.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:39.51,0:51:41.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I was very anti-religious.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:41.67,0:51:44.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Intensely anti-religious.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:44.51,0:51:49.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't hate God.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:49.07,0:51:51.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I was just anti-religious.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:51.07,0:51:53.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Absurd.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:53.32,0:51:55.32,Default,,0,0,0,,So I understand the skeptics
Dialogue: 0,0:51:55.32,0:51:57.32,Default,,0,0,0,,when they ridicule faith in God,
Dialogue: 0,0:51:57.32,0:51:59.32,Default,,0,0,0,,religion and all.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:59.32,0:52:01.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I went through it.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:01.32,0:52:03.36,Default,,0,0,0,,It's sort of an adolescent phase.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:03.36,0:52:05.36,Default,,0,0,0,,If you haven't been an atheist
Dialogue: 0,0:52:05.36,0:52:07.36,Default,,0,0,0,,in one time in adolescence,
Dialogue: 0,0:52:07.36,0:52:10.15,Default,,0,0,0,,you're probably not scheduled
Dialogue: 0,0:52:10.15,0:52:12.15,Default,,0,0,0,,for enlightenment.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:12.15,0:52:14.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:14.15,0:52:16.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Because you didn't care enough about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:16.15,0:52:18.15,Default,,0,0,0,,It's like a person who's never gotten angry
Dialogue: 0,0:52:18.15,0:52:20.15,Default,,0,0,0,,is not going to become heavenly
Dialogue: 0,0:52:20.15,0:52:22.15,Default,,0,0,0,,because if you don't care enough about life
Dialogue: 0,0:52:22.15,0:52:25.53,Default,,0,0,0,,you don't care about the facts.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:25.53,0:52:28.71,Default,,0,0,0,,There was still a drive
Dialogue: 0,0:52:28.71,0:52:30.71,Default,,0,0,0,,to know the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:30.71,0:52:32.71,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why I became an atheist.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:32.71,0:52:34.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I became an atheist because
Dialogue: 0,0:52:34.71,0:52:36.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I was driven like a mania
Dialogue: 0,0:52:36.71,0:52:38.71,Default,,0,0,0,,to discover the truth behind existence,
Dialogue: 0,0:52:38.71,0:52:40.71,Default,,0,0,0,,the truth of reality,
Dialogue: 0,0:52:40.71,0:52:44.11,Default,,0,0,0,,the truth of creation.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:44.11,0:52:46.11,Default,,0,0,0,,And the belief in God didn't serve anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:46.11,0:52:48.11,Default,,0,0,0,,So God went down
Dialogue: 0,0:52:48.11,0:52:50.11,Default,,0,0,0,,as a consequence
Dialogue: 0,0:52:50.11,0:52:52.11,Default,,0,0,0,,of my pursuit for truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:52.11,0:52:54.53,Default,,0,0,0,,And
Dialogue: 0,0:52:54.53,0:52:56.53,Default,,0,0,0,,this led to an inner search
Dialogue: 0,0:52:56.53,0:52:58.53,Default,,0,0,0,,and sort of an endless despair.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:58.53,0:53:01.11,Default,,0,0,0,,And I went to
Dialogue: 0,0:53:01.11,0:53:05.13,Default,,0,0,0,,the very bottom,
Dialogue: 0,0:53:05.13,0:53:07.13,Default,,0,0,0,,the serious source of the ego itself,
Dialogue: 0,0:53:07.13,0:53:09.13,Default,,0,0,0,,the source of human existence
Dialogue: 0,0:53:09.13,0:53:11.13,Default,,0,0,0,,and the source of human awareness
Dialogue: 0,0:53:11.13,0:53:13.13,Default,,0,0,0,,of its own existence.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:13.13,0:53:15.13,Default,,0,0,0,,So I dove into the depths
Dialogue: 0,0:53:15.13,0:53:17.13,Default,,0,0,0,,of the inner realm
Dialogue: 0,0:53:17.13,0:53:20.57,Default,,0,0,0,,of the existential self
Dialogue: 0,0:53:20.57,0:53:22.57,Default,,0,0,0,,and in searching I then went into
Dialogue: 0,0:53:22.57,0:53:25.01,Default,,0,0,0,,a state of hell.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:25.01,0:53:28.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Profound hell
Dialogue: 0,0:53:28.46,0:53:30.46,Default,,0,0,0,,of endless spiritual agony.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:30.46,0:53:33.32,Default,,0,0,0,,The upper levels of hell
Dialogue: 0,0:53:33.32,0:53:35.32,Default,,0,0,0,,are people being tortured and all that.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:35.32,0:53:37.32,Default,,0,0,0,,That's jacks for openers.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:37.32,0:53:39.32,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not even getting serious yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:39.32,0:53:42.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Beyond
Dialogue: 0,0:53:42.00,0:53:44.00,Default,,0,0,0,,the agony, beyond the
Dialogue: 0,0:53:44.00,0:53:46.00,Default,,0,0,0,,screaming torment and all that
Dialogue: 0,0:53:46.00,0:53:48.40,Default,,0,0,0,,begins the real hell.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:48.40,0:53:50.40,Default,,0,0,0,,The real hell is dread beyond
Dialogue: 0,0:53:50.40,0:53:53.05,Default,,0,0,0,,description.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:53.05,0:53:55.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Because it's characterized by an
Dialogue: 0,0:53:55.05,0:53:57.05,Default,,0,0,0,,absolute hopelessness
Dialogue: 0,0:53:57.05,0:53:59.40,Default,,0,0,0,,and you understand
Dialogue: 0,0:53:59.40,0:54:01.40,Default,,0,0,0,,what hopeless is
Dialogue: 0,0:54:01.40,0:54:03.40,Default,,0,0,0,,and you understand what forever is
Dialogue: 0,0:54:03.40,0:54:05.40,Default,,0,0,0,,because in this hope
Dialogue: 0,0:54:05.40,0:54:07.40,Default,,0,0,0,,you are condemned to this hopeless
Dialogue: 0,0:54:07.40,0:54:09.59,Default,,0,0,0,,agony forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:09.59,0:54:11.84,Default,,0,0,0,,And you get what
Dialogue: 0,0:54:11.84,0:54:13.84,Default,,0,0,0,,forever means.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:13.84,0:54:16.46,Default,,0,0,0,,And then the real dread hits.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:16.46,0:54:20.15,Default,,0,0,0,,To abandon all
Dialogue: 0,0:54:20.15,0:54:22.15,Default,,0,0,0,,hope, ye who enter here.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:22.15,0:54:24.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Dante knew that. I don't know how he knew that.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:24.15,0:54:26.15,Default,,0,0,0,,But on that level, that's
Dialogue: 0,0:54:26.15,0:54:28.15,Default,,0,0,0,,annoyingness. Once you pass
Dialogue: 0,0:54:28.15,0:54:30.53,Default,,0,0,0,,this barrier, there
Dialogue: 0,0:54:30.53,0:54:32.53,Default,,0,0,0,,is no hope for all
Dialogue: 0,0:54:32.53,0:54:34.92,Default,,0,0,0,,eternity. All
Dialogue: 0,0:54:34.92,0:54:36.92,Default,,0,0,0,,eternity. All eternity.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:36.92,0:54:38.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Forever. You realize
Dialogue: 0,0:54:38.92,0:54:40.92,Default,,0,0,0,,what that means.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:40.92,0:54:43.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Never ever will you
Dialogue: 0,0:54:43.34,0:54:45.34,Default,,0,0,0,,again have the chance to experience
Dialogue: 0,0:54:45.34,0:54:49.09,Default,,0,0,0,,the light. In the depths of
Dialogue: 0,0:54:49.09,0:54:51.09,Default,,0,0,0,,that absolute despair
Dialogue: 0,0:54:51.09,0:54:53.42,Default,,0,0,0,,which is timeless.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:53.42,0:54:55.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Just like the highest states went on
Dialogue: 0,0:54:55.42,0:54:57.42,Default,,0,0,0,,forever, this state
Dialogue: 0,0:54:57.42,0:54:59.42,Default,,0,0,0,,went on forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:59.42,0:55:02.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Eons. In the
Dialogue: 0,0:55:02.51,0:55:05.76,Default,,0,0,0,,bottom of the pit
Dialogue: 0,0:55:05.76,0:55:07.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I said, if there is a God
Dialogue: 0,0:55:07.76,0:55:10.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I ask him for help.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:10.17,0:55:12.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Then I went blank.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:12.40,0:55:15.57,Default,,0,0,0,,When they came to
Dialogue: 0,0:55:15.57,0:55:19.88,Default,,0,0,0,,me, the entire universe
Dialogue: 0,0:55:19.88,0:55:22.13,Default,,0,0,0,,had totally changed.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:22.13,0:55:24.13,Default,,0,0,0,,The exquisite presence of all
Dialogue: 0,0:55:24.13,0:55:27.90,Default,,0,0,0,,that exists as divinity.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:27.90,0:55:29.90,Default,,0,0,0,,What I'm looking at now
Dialogue: 0,0:55:29.90,0:55:32.57,Default,,0,0,0,,is divinity
Dialogue: 0,0:55:32.57,0:55:34.57,Default,,0,0,0,,expressed as all of you
Dialogue: 0,0:55:34.57,0:55:36.80,Default,,0,0,0,,here know.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:36.80,0:55:39.28,Default,,0,0,0,,The divinity of all that
Dialogue: 0,0:55:39.28,0:55:41.28,Default,,0,0,0,,exists shines forth
Dialogue: 0,0:55:41.28,0:55:43.28,Default,,0,0,0,,with a shocking emergence
Dialogue: 0,0:55:43.28,0:55:45.28,Default,,0,0,0,,beyond words, beyond description.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:45.28,0:55:47.28,Default,,0,0,0,,It's as though the
Dialogue: 0,0:55:47.28,0:55:49.28,Default,,0,0,0,,everything radiates out
Dialogue: 0,0:55:49.28,0:55:51.28,Default,,0,0,0,,the essence of that which it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:51.28,0:55:53.53,Default,,0,0,0,,The greenness of the flower
Dialogue: 0,0:55:53.53,0:55:55.53,Default,,0,0,0,,shines forth
Dialogue: 0,0:55:55.53,0:55:59.19,Default,,0,0,0,,as a presence.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:59.19,0:56:01.19,Default,,0,0,0,,The essence of all that exists
Dialogue: 0,0:56:01.19,0:56:03.19,Default,,0,0,0,,shines forth via its essence.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:03.19,0:56:05.32,Default,,0,0,0,,And you see
Dialogue: 0,0:56:05.32,0:56:07.32,Default,,0,0,0,,the divinity of all
Dialogue: 0,0:56:07.32,0:56:09.67,Default,,0,0,0,,of creation.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:09.67,0:56:11.67,Default,,0,0,0,,The essence of all
Dialogue: 0,0:56:11.67,0:56:14.28,Default,,0,0,0,,that exists is divine.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:14.28,0:56:16.28,Default,,0,0,0,,So when we lick our attachments
Dialogue: 0,0:56:16.28,0:56:18.28,Default,,0,0,0,,to the linear perception
Dialogue: 0,0:56:18.28,0:56:20.59,Default,,0,0,0,,then you become aware
Dialogue: 0,0:56:20.59,0:56:22.59,Default,,0,0,0,,of the divinity
Dialogue: 0,0:56:22.59,0:56:24.59,Default,,0,0,0,,of the essence of all
Dialogue: 0,0:56:24.59,0:56:26.59,Default,,0,0,0,,that exists.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:26.59,0:56:33.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Therefore,
Dialogue: 0,0:56:33.46,0:56:36.01,Default,,0,0,0,,your life is conducted
Dialogue: 0,0:56:36.01,0:56:38.11,Default,,0,0,0,,at all times
Dialogue: 0,0:56:38.11,0:56:40.11,Default,,0,0,0,,in the presence of God.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:42.17,0:56:44.17,Default,,0,0,0,,At all times you are in
Dialogue: 0,0:56:44.17,0:56:46.17,Default,,0,0,0,,the presence of God.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:46.17,0:56:49.13,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just that you fail to recognize it.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:51.23,0:56:53.23,Default,,0,0,0,,And when you recognize it
Dialogue: 0,0:56:53.23,0:56:55.23,Default,,0,0,0,,you see the divinity of all that exists.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:55.23,0:56:57.84,Default,,0,0,0,,The infinite potential
Dialogue: 0,0:56:57.84,0:56:59.90,Default,,0,0,0,,of creation.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:59.90,0:57:01.90,Default,,0,0,0,,You see that evolution and creation
Dialogue: 0,0:57:01.90,0:57:04.09,Default,,0,0,0,,are one and the same thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:04.09,0:57:06.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Evolution is what creation looks like.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:06.09,0:57:09.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Religionists tend to think
Dialogue: 0,0:57:09.34,0:57:11.34,Default,,0,0,0,,there was a God.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:11.34,0:57:13.34,Default,,0,0,0,,First there was nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:13.34,0:57:15.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Then suddenly there was a God.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:15.76,0:57:17.76,Default,,0,0,0,,He rolled out the dice
Dialogue: 0,0:57:17.76,0:57:20.78,Default,,0,0,0,,and then he took off on vacation.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:23.42,0:57:27.40,Default,,0,0,0,,So the bottom-up theory
Dialogue: 0,0:57:27.40,0:57:29.40,Default,,0,0,0,,of creation and the top-down
Dialogue: 0,0:57:29.40,0:57:31.40,Default,,0,0,0,,theories of creation
Dialogue: 0,0:57:31.40,0:57:33.40,Default,,0,0,0,,are still looking at God
Dialogue: 0,0:57:33.40,0:57:35.40,Default,,0,0,0,,and that which is forever
Dialogue: 0,0:57:35.40,0:57:37.55,Default,,0,0,0,,has no beginning.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:37.55,0:57:39.55,Default,,0,0,0,,It has no ending.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:39.55,0:57:41.55,Default,,0,0,0,,It has no start.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:41.55,0:57:45.13,Default,,0,0,0,,It has no source.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:45.13,0:57:47.13,Default,,0,0,0,,It has no cause.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:47.13,0:57:50.00,Default,,0,0,0,,There is no first principle to God.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:50.00,0:57:52.00,Default,,0,0,0,,That which has been forever
Dialogue: 0,0:57:52.00,0:57:54.00,Default,,0,0,0,,has no beginning.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:54.00,0:57:56.00,Default,,0,0,0,,So there's no point to look
Dialogue: 0,0:57:56.00,0:57:58.00,Default,,0,0,0,,for the cause of the beginning
Dialogue: 0,0:57:58.00,0:58:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,which is bad enough to look
Dialogue: 0,0:58:00.00,0:58:02.00,Default,,0,0,0,,for cause in the Newtonian dimension
Dialogue: 0,0:58:02.00,0:58:04.00,Default,,0,0,0,,of the mid-400s
Dialogue: 0,0:58:04.00,0:58:06.00,Default,,0,0,0,,when spiritual realities don't get serious
Dialogue: 0,0:58:06.00,0:58:08.11,Default,,0,0,0,,over and over.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:08.11,0:58:10.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright, so let's go
Dialogue: 0,0:58:10.11,0:58:12.86,Default,,0,0,0,,and you'll have to let me know
Dialogue: 0,0:58:12.86,0:58:14.92,Default,,0,0,0,,when it's break time.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:14.92,0:58:17.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh good, alright.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:17.07,0:58:19.07,Default,,0,0,0,,So we were just saying
Dialogue: 0,0:58:19.07,0:58:21.07,Default,,0,0,0,,what got me going on this whole thing
Dialogue: 0,0:58:21.07,0:58:23.55,Default,,0,0,0,,was the archangel.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:23.55,0:58:25.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, I lost my place here somewhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:25.55,0:58:27.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I got up to archangel
Dialogue: 0,0:58:27.63,0:58:29.63,Default,,0,0,0,,and next thing you know
Dialogue: 0,0:58:29.63,0:58:32.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I took off in a different realm.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:32.13,0:58:34.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Archangels calibrate 50,000 and up.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:34.19,0:58:36.32,Default,,0,0,0,,So
Dialogue: 0,0:58:36.32,0:58:39.36,Default,,0,0,0,,in the pit of hell
Dialogue: 0,0:58:39.36,0:58:41.36,Default,,0,0,0,,which I don't know how I got there
Dialogue: 0,0:58:41.36,0:58:46.19,Default,,0,0,0,,but I got there
Dialogue: 0,0:58:46.19,0:58:48.19,Default,,0,0,0,,the prayer went up.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:48.19,0:58:50.19,Default,,0,0,0,,If there is a God I hear him
Dialogue: 0,0:58:50.19,0:58:52.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I ask him for help.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:52.55,0:58:54.55,Default,,0,0,0,,At that level of hell apparently
Dialogue: 0,0:58:54.55,0:58:56.65,Default,,0,0,0,,it takes an archangel to pay attention to you
Dialogue: 0,0:58:56.65,0:58:58.65,Default,,0,0,0,,because an archangel paid attention
Dialogue: 0,0:58:58.65,0:59:03.53,Default,,0,0,0,,to the thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:03.53,0:59:05.53,Default,,0,0,0,,That archangel calibrated 50,000.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:05.53,0:59:10.40,Default,,0,0,0,,We're talking a lot of rhythmic.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:10.40,0:59:14.01,Default,,0,0,0,,That's a lot of juice, 50,000.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:19.61,0:59:21.61,Default,,0,0,0,,So I pictured this archangel
Dialogue: 0,0:59:21.61,0:59:24.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I heard this goofball
Dialogue: 0,0:59:24.63,0:59:26.63,Default,,0,0,0,,agonizing
Dialogue: 0,0:59:26.63,0:59:29.30,Default,,0,0,0,,with his karmic watch and said
Dialogue: 0,0:59:29.30,0:59:34.05,Default,,0,0,0,,and out of that came the transformation
Dialogue: 0,0:59:34.05,0:59:36.05,Default,,0,0,0,,that stands before you
Dialogue: 0,0:59:36.05,0:59:46.05,Default,,0,0,0,,this day.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:46.05,0:59:49.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't mess with archangels.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:49.11,0:59:54.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't mess with archangels.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:54.53,0:59:56.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright, we'll go on to the next slide.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:56.53,0:59:59.05,Default,,0,0,0,,This is just a calibration
Dialogue: 0,0:59:59.05,1:00:01.05,Default,,0,0,0,,of the energy
Dialogue: 0,1:00:01.05,1:00:03.05,Default,,0,0,0,,somebody figured out mathematically
Dialogue: 0,1:00:03.05,1:00:05.05,Default,,0,0,0,,the relative energies
Dialogue: 0,1:00:05.05,1:00:07.05,Default,,0,0,0,,as you go up the scale of consciousness.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:07.05,1:00:09.63,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll go to the next one.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:09.63,1:00:12.67,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the distribution
Dialogue: 0,1:00:12.67,1:00:14.67,Default,,0,0,0,,of the level of consciousness
Dialogue: 0,1:00:14.67,1:00:16.67,Default,,0,0,0,,which helps you understand this world.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:16.67,1:00:18.67,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no point of bemoaning this world
Dialogue: 0,1:00:18.67,1:00:21.26,Default,,0,0,0,,when you see that
Dialogue: 0,1:00:21.26,1:00:23.26,Default,,0,0,0,,approximately 80% of the world's population
Dialogue: 0,1:00:23.26,1:00:25.26,Default,,0,0,0,,calibrates below 200.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:25.26,1:00:27.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Therefore
Dialogue: 0,1:00:27.80,1:00:29.80,Default,,0,0,0,,truth does not prevail
Dialogue: 0,1:00:29.80,1:00:31.80,Default,,0,0,0,,in 80% of mankind.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:31.80,1:00:34.98,Default,,0,0,0,,You want to negotiate
Dialogue: 0,1:00:34.98,1:00:36.98,Default,,0,0,0,,with people who don't believe in honesty or truth?
Dialogue: 0,1:00:36.98,1:00:39.46,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what we're trying to do
Dialogue: 0,1:00:39.46,1:00:41.46,Default,,0,0,0,,all over the world all the time.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:41.46,1:00:43.69,Default,,0,0,0,,They think it'd be good
Dialogue: 0,1:00:43.69,1:00:45.84,Default,,0,0,0,,if mankind is just stupid.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:48.55,1:00:51.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright, so
Dialogue: 0,1:00:51.03,1:00:53.09,Default,,0,0,0,,this is the mass of mankind.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:53.09,1:00:55.09,Default,,0,0,0,,So you see the levels
Dialogue: 0,1:00:55.09,1:00:57.09,Default,,0,0,0,,here, how few people there are
Dialogue: 0,1:00:57.09,1:00:59.09,Default,,0,0,0,,even at the level of the intellect, 400.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:59.09,1:01:01.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Certainly the mid-intellect
Dialogue: 0,1:01:01.09,1:01:03.09,Default,,0,0,0,,500 people that are motivated
Dialogue: 0,1:01:03.09,1:01:05.09,Default,,0,0,0,,by lovingness
Dialogue: 0,1:01:05.09,1:01:07.09,Default,,0,0,0,,and you see that enlightenment
Dialogue: 0,1:01:07.09,1:01:09.13,Default,,0,0,0,,is almost an impossibility.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:09.13,1:01:11.13,Default,,0,0,0,,There are only a couple of people on the planet
Dialogue: 0,1:01:11.13,1:01:13.28,Default,,0,0,0,,at any one time
Dialogue: 0,1:01:13.28,1:01:15.32,Default,,0,0,0,,in the higher levels.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:15.32,1:01:17.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Unconditional love
Dialogue: 0,1:01:17.32,1:01:19.32,Default,,0,0,0,,the 12 step groups
Dialogue: 0,1:01:19.32,1:01:21.48,Default,,0,0,0,,0.4%
Dialogue: 0,1:01:21.48,1:01:23.71,Default,,0,0,0,,and only a few
Dialogue: 0,1:01:23.71,1:01:25.71,Default,,0,0,0,,people ever hit 600
Dialogue: 0,1:01:25.71,1:01:27.71,Default,,0,0,0,,which is the level of
Dialogue: 0,1:01:27.71,1:01:29.71,Default,,0,0,0,,divine infinite bliss
Dialogue: 0,1:01:29.71,1:01:31.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Sat Chit Ananda
Dialogue: 0,1:01:31.73,1:01:33.73,Default,,0,0,0,,and half of them leave at that point.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:33.73,1:01:36.28,Default,,0,0,0,,There are very few left
Dialogue: 0,1:01:36.28,1:01:38.28,Default,,0,0,0,,because half leave at 600
Dialogue: 0,1:01:38.28,1:01:41.11,Default,,0,0,0,,and as it goes up, half leave.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:41.11,1:01:43.11,Default,,0,0,0,,One characteristic of those states
Dialogue: 0,1:01:43.11,1:01:46.51,Default,,0,0,0,,is the state of infinite wonderment
Dialogue: 0,1:01:46.51,1:01:48.51,Default,,0,0,0,,and bliss and complete and total
Dialogue: 0,1:01:48.51,1:01:50.94,Default,,0,0,0,,there's nothing you want
Dialogue: 0,1:01:50.94,1:01:52.94,Default,,0,0,0,,there's nothing you need
Dialogue: 0,1:01:52.94,1:01:54.94,Default,,0,0,0,,your condition is complete and total
Dialogue: 0,1:01:54.94,1:01:57.38,Default,,0,0,0,,and fine
Dialogue: 0,1:01:57.38,1:01:59.38,Default,,0,0,0,,and if the body topples over
Dialogue: 0,1:01:59.38,1:02:01.38,Default,,0,0,0,,you have a strange
Dialogue: 0,1:02:01.38,1:02:03.38,Default,,0,0,0,,there's a strange permission to leave
Dialogue: 0,1:02:03.38,1:02:05.55,Default,,0,0,0,,and it recurs every once in a while
Dialogue: 0,1:02:05.55,1:02:07.55,Default,,0,0,0,,sometimes very unexpectedly
Dialogue: 0,1:02:07.55,1:02:09.55,Default,,0,0,0,,suddenly the state of bliss
Dialogue: 0,1:02:09.55,1:02:11.55,Default,,0,0,0,,just becomes overwhelming
Dialogue: 0,1:02:11.55,1:02:13.55,Default,,0,0,0,,and you could leave
Dialogue: 0,1:02:13.55,1:02:15.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I could have left this morning
Dialogue: 0,1:02:15.55,1:02:17.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm walking around
Dialogue: 0,1:02:17.55,1:02:19.55,Default,,0,0,0,,and we're all breaking down with tears of joy
Dialogue: 0,1:02:19.55,1:02:21.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I just left
Dialogue: 0,1:02:21.55,1:02:24.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I had permission to leave
Dialogue: 0,1:02:24.69,1:02:28.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I could go
Dialogue: 0,1:02:28.03,1:02:30.03,Default,,0,0,0,,but then what about the people
Dialogue: 0,1:02:30.03,1:02:33.19,Default,,0,0,0,,sitting around waiting for you to talk
Dialogue: 0,1:02:33.19,1:02:35.19,Default,,0,0,0,,it's always something
Dialogue: 0,1:02:35.19,1:02:38.34,Default,,0,0,0,,something
Dialogue: 0,1:02:38.34,1:02:40.34,Default,,0,0,0,,duck pecking at your ankle
Dialogue: 0,1:02:40.34,1:02:43.17,Default,,0,0,0,,okay
Dialogue: 0,1:02:43.17,1:02:45.30,Default,,0,0,0,,well
Dialogue: 0,1:02:45.30,1:02:47.30,Default,,0,0,0,,because of the people's love
Dialogue: 0,1:02:47.30,1:02:49.30,Default,,0,0,0,,you can't leave them
Dialogue: 0,1:02:49.30,1:02:51.94,Default,,0,0,0,,that's what it's about
Dialogue: 0,1:02:51.94,1:02:57.17,Default,,0,0,0,,so
Dialogue: 0,1:02:57.17,1:02:59.17,Default,,0,0,0,,you continue to live
Dialogue: 0,1:02:59.17,1:03:01.17,Default,,0,0,0,,so here's the distribution of mankind
Dialogue: 0,1:03:01.17,1:03:03.17,Default,,0,0,0,,you understand now
Dialogue: 0,1:03:03.17,1:03:05.17,Default,,0,0,0,,the evening paper
Dialogue: 0,1:03:05.17,1:03:07.17,Default,,0,0,0,,and the news
