Dialogue: 0,1:03:21.65,1:03:23.65,Default,,0,0,0,,a reinforcement of their preference
Dialogue: 0,1:03:23.65,1:03:25.65,Default,,0,0,0,,they want you to prove
Dialogue: 0,1:03:25.65,1:03:27.65,Default,,0,0,0,,that what they believe in is true
Dialogue: 0,1:03:27.65,1:03:29.65,Default,,0,0,0,,so people who can't do kinesiology
Dialogue: 0,1:03:29.65,1:03:31.65,Default,,0,0,0,,can't do it
Dialogue: 0,1:03:31.65,1:03:33.65,Default,,0,0,0,,because they cannot seem to detach
Dialogue: 0,1:03:33.65,1:03:36.13,Default,,0,0,0,,and become objective
