Dialogue: 0,1:03:38.13,1:03:40.13,Default,,0,0,0,,first let's see what the truth is
Dialogue: 0,1:03:40.13,1:03:42.13,Default,,0,0,0,,and then I'll decide what I want to do about it
Dialogue: 0,1:03:42.13,1:03:44.13,Default,,0,0,0,,but no they don't want to do it that way
Dialogue: 0,1:03:44.13,1:03:46.13,Default,,0,0,0,,they want to rig the bet
Dialogue: 0,1:03:46.13,1:03:48.13,Default,,0,0,0,,so that they find reinforcement
Dialogue: 0,1:03:48.13,1:03:50.71,Default,,0,0,0,,of what they want to believe
Dialogue: 0,1:03:50.71,1:03:53.57,Default,,0,0,0,,alright we'll move on
Dialogue: 0,1:03:53.57,1:03:55.57,Default,,0,0,0,,so you see the power
Dialogue: 0,1:03:55.57,1:03:57.57,Default,,0,0,0,,it's the power of these people here
