Dialogue: 0,1:03:59.57,1:04:01.57,Default,,0,0,0,,you say why doesn't the world self-destruct
Dialogue: 0,1:04:01.57,1:04:03.57,Default,,0,0,0,,make energy
Dialogue: 0,1:04:03.57,1:04:05.57,Default,,0,0,0,,so these people are numerous
