Dialogue: 0,1:04:43.53,1:04:45.53,Default,,0,0,0,,right during a class
Dialogue: 0,1:04:45.53,1:04:47.53,Default,,0,0,0,,we clocked it
Dialogue: 0,1:04:47.53,1:04:49.53,Default,,0,0,0,,right during the class Harmonic Concordance
Dialogue: 0,1:04:49.53,1:04:51.94,Default,,0,0,0,,remember it went up
Dialogue: 0,1:04:51.94,1:04:53.94,Default,,0,0,0,,and I was a little disappointed
Dialogue: 0,1:04:53.94,1:04:55.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought it was going to continue up
Dialogue: 0,1:04:55.94,1:04:58.23,Default,,0,0,0,,no it went back down again
Dialogue: 0,1:04:58.23,1:05:00.23,Default,,0,0,0,,so what's America right now
Dialogue: 0,1:05:00.23,1:05:02.32,Default,,0,0,0,,let's see America right now
