Dialogue: 0,1:05:04.32,1:05:06.32,Default,,0,0,0,,oops 421
Dialogue: 0,1:05:06.32,1:05:08.51,Default,,0,0,0,,America right now is over 420
Dialogue: 0,1:05:08.51,1:05:10.84,Default,,0,0,0,,421
Dialogue: 0,1:05:10.84,1:05:12.84,Default,,0,0,0,,it went down again
Dialogue: 0,1:05:12.84,1:05:15.63,Default,,0,0,0,,420
Dialogue: 0,1:05:15.63,1:05:17.71,Default,,0,0,0,,426 it was 426
Dialogue: 0,1:05:17.71,1:05:21.53,Default,,0,0,0,,well
Dialogue: 0,1:05:21.53,1:05:28.51,Default,,0,0,0,,you bad folks better quit sinning out there
Dialogue: 0,1:05:30.90,1:05:33.80,Default,,0,0,0,,alright so mankind
Dialogue: 0,1:05:33.80,1:05:35.80,Default,,0,0,0,,we'll get to mankind in a while
Dialogue: 0,1:05:35.80,1:05:38.51,Default,,0,0,0,,we'll move on
Dialogue: 0,1:05:38.51,1:05:40.73,Default,,0,0,0,,let's move on to the next one
Dialogue: 0,1:05:40.73,1:05:42.73,Default,,0,0,0,,this is the percent of elapsed time
Dialogue: 0,1:05:42.73,1:05:44.92,Default,,0,0,0,,the level of consciousness
Dialogue: 0,1:05:44.92,1:05:47.55,Default,,0,0,0,,we'll go to the next one
Dialogue: 0,1:05:47.55,1:05:49.55,Default,,0,0,0,,those of us who have been here before
Dialogue: 0,1:05:49.55,1:05:53.82,Default,,0,0,0,,this is tracing the evolution of consciousness over time
Dialogue: 0,1:05:53.82,1:05:55.82,Default,,0,0,0,,over great eons of time
Dialogue: 0,1:05:55.82,1:05:58.13,Default,,0,0,0,,you see the light
Dialogue: 0,1:05:58.13,1:06:00.13,Default,,0,0,0,,of divinity
Dialogue: 0,1:06:00.13,1:06:02.13,Default,,0,0,0,,there's first the Godhead
Dialogue: 0,1:06:02.13,1:06:04.40,Default,,0,0,0,,out of which emerges God
Dialogue: 0,1:06:04.40,1:06:06.40,Default,,0,0,0,,out of which emerges creation
Dialogue: 0,1:06:06.40,1:06:08.48,Default,,0,0,0,,which shines forth as the radiation
Dialogue: 0,1:06:08.48,1:06:10.48,Default,,0,0,0,,the infinite power
Dialogue: 0,1:06:10.48,1:06:12.48,Default,,0,0,0,,of consciousness
Dialogue: 0,1:06:12.48,1:06:14.80,Default,,0,0,0,,and when consciousness
Dialogue: 0,1:06:14.80,1:06:16.80,Default,,0,0,0,,interacts with
Dialogue: 0,1:06:16.80,1:06:18.80,Default,,0,0,0,,any matter
Dialogue: 0,1:06:18.80,1:06:21.38,Default,,0,0,0,,it emerges as life
Dialogue: 0,1:06:21.38,1:06:23.38,Default,,0,0,0,,life itself cannot be destroyed
Dialogue: 0,1:06:23.38,1:06:25.63,Default,,0,0,0,,let's get that one
Dialogue: 0,1:06:25.63,1:06:27.63,Default,,0,0,0,,for sure
Dialogue: 0,1:06:27.63,1:06:29.63,Default,,0,0,0,,life itself cannot be destroyed
Dialogue: 0,1:06:29.63,1:06:31.63,Default,,0,0,0,,resist
Dialogue: 0,1:06:31.63,1:06:33.84,Default,,0,0,0,,so you can quit worrying about death
Dialogue: 0,1:06:33.84,1:06:35.84,Default,,0,0,0,,because there isn't any
Dialogue: 0,1:06:35.84,1:06:37.84,Default,,0,0,0,,life cannot be destroyed
Dialogue: 0,1:06:37.84,1:06:40.67,Default,,0,0,0,,the law of conservation of energy
Dialogue: 0,1:06:40.67,1:06:42.67,Default,,0,0,0,,the law of conservation of matter
Dialogue: 0,1:06:42.67,1:06:44.67,Default,,0,0,0,,and it just amazes me
Dialogue: 0,1:06:44.67,1:06:46.67,Default,,0,0,0,,the law of conservation of life
Dialogue: 0,1:06:46.67,1:06:48.92,Default,,0,0,0,,you can make life
Dialogue: 0,1:06:48.92,1:06:50.92,Default,,0,0,0,,change form
Dialogue: 0,1:06:50.92,1:06:53.50,Default,,0,0,0,,but you cannot kill it
Dialogue: 0,1:06:53.50,1:06:55.50,Default,,0,0,0,,so you can stop feeling guilty
Dialogue: 0,1:06:55.50,1:06:58.67,Default,,0,0,0,,about swatting flies
Dialogue: 0,1:06:58.67,1:07:00.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I was an intensive Buddhist for a long time
Dialogue: 0,1:07:00.67,1:07:02.88,Default,,0,0,0,,and the patient would leave my office
Dialogue: 0,1:07:02.88,1:07:04.88,Default,,0,0,0,,and I had a
Dialogue: 0,1:07:04.88,1:07:06.88,Default,,0,0,0,,butterfly net behind the drapes
Dialogue: 0,1:07:06.88,1:07:08.88,Default,,0,0,0,,as soon as the patient
Dialogue: 0,1:07:08.88,1:07:10.88,Default,,0,0,0,,we did a 50 minute hour
Dialogue: 0,1:07:10.88,1:07:12.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I take this thing out
Dialogue: 0,1:07:12.88,1:07:14.88,Default,,0,0,0,,and I catch these flies in the middle
Dialogue: 0,1:07:14.88,1:07:16.88,Default,,0,0,0,,and I put them out the window
Dialogue: 0,1:07:16.88,1:07:18.88,Default,,0,0,0,,because I didn't want to kill a fly
Dialogue: 0,1:07:18.88,1:07:20.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't want a patient seeing me do that
Dialogue: 0,1:07:20.88,1:07:23.61,Default,,0,0,0,,they didn't know I was a Buddhist
Dialogue: 0,1:07:23.61,1:07:25.61,Default,,0,0,0,,and I didn't believe in killing anything
Dialogue: 0,1:07:25.61,1:07:27.61,Default,,0,0,0,,including flies
Dialogue: 0,1:07:29.76,1:07:32.19,Default,,0,0,0,,well
Dialogue: 0,1:07:32.19,1:07:34.38,Default,,0,0,0,,let's see what actually happens
Dialogue: 0,1:07:34.38,1:07:36.38,Default,,0,0,0,,when you kill a fly
Dialogue: 0,1:07:36.38,1:07:38.38,Default,,0,0,0,,it doesn't even notice it
Dialogue: 0,1:07:38.38,1:07:40.51,Default,,0,0,0,,you kill a fly
Dialogue: 0,1:07:40.51,1:07:43.15,Default,,0,0,0,,it doesn't even notice it
Dialogue: 0,1:07:43.15,1:07:45.15,Default,,0,0,0,,it goes right along flying
Dialogue: 0,1:07:45.15,1:07:47.15,Default,,0,0,0,,in its etheric body
Dialogue: 0,1:07:47.15,1:07:50.55,Default,,0,0,0,,and it doesn't realize anything has changed
Dialogue: 0,1:07:50.55,1:07:52.55,Default,,0,0,0,,the fact that you don't see it
Dialogue: 0,1:07:52.55,1:07:54.55,Default,,0,0,0,,is not his problem
Dialogue: 0,1:07:54.55,1:08:00.78,Default,,0,0,0,,those of you who have been out of body
Dialogue: 0,1:08:00.78,1:08:02.78,Default,,0,0,0,,know what I am talking about
Dialogue: 0,1:08:02.78,1:08:05.36,Default,,0,0,0,,you go out of body
Dialogue: 0,1:08:05.36,1:08:07.36,Default,,0,0,0,,it happened to me spontaneously
Dialogue: 0,1:08:07.36,1:08:09.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I never heard about it
Dialogue: 0,1:08:09.36,1:08:11.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I was sick as a dog
Dialogue: 0,1:08:11.36,1:08:13.36,Default,,0,0,0,,and there I am suddenly
Dialogue: 0,1:08:13.36,1:08:16.38,Default,,0,0,0,,ten feet over my body
Dialogue: 0,1:08:16.38,1:08:18.38,Default,,0,0,0,,there is Dave up in the air
Dialogue: 0,1:08:18.38,1:08:20.38,Default,,0,0,0,,no there is Dave down there
Dialogue: 0,1:08:20.38,1:08:22.69,Default,,0,0,0,,there is me
Dialogue: 0,1:08:22.69,1:08:24.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I can hear
Dialogue: 0,1:08:24.69,1:08:26.69,Default,,0,0,0,,when you are out of body
Dialogue: 0,1:08:26.69,1:08:28.92,Default,,0,0,0,,you can see, think, feel, hear
Dialogue: 0,1:08:28.92,1:08:30.92,Default,,0,0,0,,all the senses are operative
Dialogue: 0,1:08:30.92,1:08:33.31,Default,,0,0,0,,how can that be
Dialogue: 0,1:08:33.31,1:08:35.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I am way up here in the room
Dialogue: 0,1:08:35.31,1:08:37.31,Default,,0,0,0,,the body is over there
Dialogue: 0,1:08:37.31,1:08:39.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I can hear, think, feel
Dialogue: 0,1:08:39.31,1:08:43.47,Default,,0,0,0,,everything perfectly
Dialogue: 0,1:08:43.47,1:08:45.47,Default,,0,0,0,,didn't even notice it
Dialogue: 0,1:08:45.47,1:08:47.47,Default,,0,0,0,,one minute you are in the body
Dialogue: 0,1:08:47.47,1:08:50.00,Default,,0,0,0,,the next minute you are out
Dialogue: 0,1:08:50.00,1:08:52.00,Default,,0,0,0,,you have no point of worrying about it
Dialogue: 0,1:08:52.00,1:08:54.31,Default,,0,0,0,,ok
Dialogue: 0,1:08:54.31,1:08:56.31,Default,,0,0,0,,we see how consciousness evolved
Dialogue: 0,1:08:56.31,1:08:58.64,Default,,0,0,0,,over great eons of time
Dialogue: 0,1:08:58.64,1:09:00.64,Default,,0,0,0,,the light of divinity
Dialogue: 0,1:09:00.64,1:09:02.64,Default,,0,0,0,,shining forth as the energy field
Dialogue: 0,1:09:02.64,1:09:04.64,Default,,0,0,0,,consciousness itself
Dialogue: 0,1:09:04.64,1:09:06.64,Default,,0,0,0,,accompanies
Dialogue: 0,1:09:06.64,1:09:09.72,Default,,0,0,0,,enters organic matter
Dialogue: 0,1:09:09.72,1:09:11.72,Default,,0,0,0,,the lowest level of consciousness
Dialogue: 0,1:09:11.72,1:09:13.72,Default,,0,0,0,,is that we can find
Dialogue: 0,1:09:13.72,1:09:15.72,Default,,0,0,0,,what calibrates as one
Dialogue: 0,1:09:15.72,1:09:18.14,Default,,0,0,0,,is that of the bacteria
Dialogue: 0,1:09:18.14,1:09:20.14,Default,,0,0,0,,then you see the evolution of consciousness
Dialogue: 0,1:09:20.14,1:09:22.14,Default,,0,0,0,,through the animal kingdom
Dialogue: 0,1:09:22.14,1:09:25.10,Default,,0,0,0,,over great periods of time
Dialogue: 0,1:09:25.10,1:09:29.27,Default,,0,0,0,,don't let me forget the bacteria
Dialogue: 0,1:09:29.27,1:09:31.27,Default,,0,0,0,,later
Dialogue: 0,1:09:34.01,1:09:36.59,Default,,0,0,0,,now here we go
Dialogue: 0,1:09:36.59,1:09:38.59,Default,,0,0,0,,over millions of earth ages
Dialogue: 0,1:09:38.59,1:09:40.59,Default,,0,0,0,,and we see
Dialogue: 0,1:09:40.59,1:09:42.59,Default,,0,0,0,,we see the reptiles
Dialogue: 0,1:09:42.59,1:09:44.59,Default,,0,0,0,,the dinosaurs
Dialogue: 0,1:09:44.59,1:09:46.59,Default,,0,0,0,,we see the calibrated level of life
Dialogue: 0,1:09:46.59,1:09:49.28,Default,,0,0,0,,in these various epochs
Dialogue: 0,1:09:49.28,1:09:51.28,Default,,0,0,0,,it rises
Dialogue: 0,1:09:51.28,1:09:53.28,Default,,0,0,0,,let's move on to the next one
Dialogue: 0,1:09:53.28,1:09:55.28,Default,,0,0,0,,it rises through the animal kingdom
Dialogue: 0,1:09:55.28,1:09:57.28,Default,,0,0,0,,rises through the animal
Dialogue: 0,1:09:57.28,1:09:59.28,Default,,0,0,0,,we are tracing the evolution of consciousness
Dialogue: 0,1:09:59.28,1:10:01.28,Default,,0,0,0,,the spirit, the soul, the essence
Dialogue: 0,1:10:01.28,1:10:03.28,Default,,0,0,0,,of life itself
Dialogue: 0,1:10:03.28,1:10:05.28,Default,,0,0,0,,goes through these various forms
Dialogue: 0,1:10:05.28,1:10:07.28,Default,,0,0,0,,there is bacteria
Dialogue: 0,1:10:07.28,1:10:09.28,Default,,0,0,0,,etwan
Dialogue: 0,1:10:09.28,1:10:11.28,Default,,0,0,0,,then protozoa, crustaceans, insects
Dialogue: 0,1:10:11.28,1:10:14.02,Default,,0,0,0,,octopuses
Dialogue: 0,1:10:14.02,1:10:16.02,Default,,0,0,0,,those are the most amazing animals
Dialogue: 0,1:10:16.02,1:10:18.02,Default,,0,0,0,,sharks, vipers
Dialogue: 0,1:10:18.02,1:10:20.02,Default,,0,0,0,,can you imagine somebody put his foot in
Dialogue: 0,1:10:20.02,1:10:22.02,Default,,0,0,0,,the pen of a komodo dragon
Dialogue: 0,1:10:22.02,1:10:24.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I think he did it in California
Dialogue: 0,1:10:26.06,1:10:29.34,Default,,0,0,0,,then we get the predatory mammals
Dialogue: 0,1:10:29.34,1:10:31.34,Default,,0,0,0,,alligators
Dialogue: 0,1:10:31.34,1:10:34.07,Default,,0,0,0,,whales
Dialogue: 0,1:10:34.07,1:10:36.07,Default,,0,0,0,,we move up through
Dialogue: 0,1:10:36.07,1:10:41.05,Default,,0,0,0,,what?
Dialogue: 0,1:10:41.05,1:10:43.05,Default,,0,0,0,,we don't want to hear about dolphins
Dialogue: 0,1:10:43.05,1:10:45.05,Default,,0,0,0,,and whales please
Dialogue: 0,1:10:45.05,1:10:47.05,Default,,0,0,0,,we don't want any more emails
Dialogue: 0,1:10:47.05,1:10:49.05,Default,,0,0,0,,one caliber is higher than the other
Dialogue: 0,1:10:49.05,1:10:52.35,Default,,0,0,0,,ask your mother
Dialogue: 0,1:10:52.35,1:10:54.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know
Dialogue: 0,1:10:54.35,1:10:56.35,Default,,0,0,0,,ask God don't ask me
Dialogue: 0,1:10:56.35,1:11:02.56,Default,,0,0,0,,ok so you'll notice
Dialogue: 0,1:11:02.56,1:11:04.56,Default,,0,0,0,,these are primarily predators
Dialogue: 0,1:11:04.56,1:11:06.77,Default,,0,0,0,,are they not
Dialogue: 0,1:11:06.77,1:11:08.77,Default,,0,0,0,,hippopotamuses kill a lot of people
Dialogue: 0,1:11:08.77,1:11:10.77,Default,,0,0,0,,you wouldn't think so
Dialogue: 0,1:11:10.77,1:11:14.43,Default,,0,0,0,,they don't look smart enough
Dialogue: 0,1:11:14.43,1:11:16.43,Default,,0,0,0,,below 200
Dialogue: 0,1:11:16.43,1:11:18.43,Default,,0,0,0,,life is lived by virtue
Dialogue: 0,1:11:18.43,1:11:20.43,Default,,0,0,0,,of the death of others
Dialogue: 0,1:11:20.43,1:11:22.43,Default,,0,0,0,,the dinosaur has to kill others to eat
Dialogue: 0,1:11:22.43,1:11:24.43,Default,,0,0,0,,the tiger has to
Dialogue: 0,1:11:24.43,1:11:26.67,Default,,0,0,0,,so below 200
Dialogue: 0,1:11:26.67,1:11:28.67,Default,,0,0,0,,is predatory
Dialogue: 0,1:11:28.67,1:11:30.67,Default,,0,0,0,,in the animal world
Dialogue: 0,1:11:30.67,1:11:32.67,Default,,0,0,0,,also in the human world
Dialogue: 0,1:11:32.67,1:11:34.85,Default,,0,0,0,,below 200 is predatory
Dialogue: 0,1:11:34.85,1:11:36.85,Default,,0,0,0,,it reacts
Dialogue: 0,1:11:36.85,1:11:38.85,Default,,0,0,0,,like an instinctual animal
Dialogue: 0,1:11:38.85,1:11:40.89,Default,,0,0,0,,game
Dialogue: 0,1:11:40.89,1:11:42.89,Default,,0,0,0,,and if you have to lose your life
Dialogue: 0,1:11:42.89,1:11:46.27,Default,,0,0,0,,too bad
Dialogue: 0,1:11:46.27,1:11:48.27,Default,,0,0,0,,then at consciousness level 200
Dialogue: 0,1:11:48.27,1:11:51.64,Default,,0,0,0,,we see a shift
Dialogue: 0,1:11:51.64,1:11:53.64,Default,,0,0,0,,from that which lives carnivorously
Dialogue: 0,1:11:53.64,1:11:55.64,Default,,0,0,0,,to the herbivore
Dialogue: 0,1:11:55.64,1:11:57.64,Default,,0,0,0,,the zebra
Dialogue: 0,1:11:57.64,1:12:00.64,Default,,0,0,0,,the giraffe
Dialogue: 0,1:12:00.64,1:12:02.80,Default,,0,0,0,,the deer
Dialogue: 0,1:12:02.80,1:12:06.03,Default,,0,0,0,,the bison
Dialogue: 0,1:12:06.03,1:12:08.03,Default,,0,0,0,,piggies, elk, sheep
Dialogue: 0,1:12:08.03,1:12:10.03,Default,,0,0,0,,you see they live
Dialogue: 0,1:12:10.03,1:12:12.03,Default,,0,0,0,,not by the death of others
Dialogue: 0,1:12:12.03,1:12:14.03,Default,,0,0,0,,in fact they fertilize everything
Dialogue: 0,1:12:14.03,1:12:16.03,Default,,0,0,0,,that furnishes the source of life for others
Dialogue: 0,1:12:16.03,1:12:18.03,Default,,0,0,0,,and we move up to
Dialogue: 0,1:12:18.03,1:12:20.03,Default,,0,0,0,,kitties at 240
Dialogue: 0,1:12:20.03,1:12:22.03,Default,,0,0,0,,family kitties
Dialogue: 0,1:12:22.03,1:12:24.03,Default,,0,0,0,,race horses, dogs, family dogs
Dialogue: 0,1:12:24.03,1:12:26.03,Default,,0,0,0,,we move up to the highest levels
Dialogue: 0,1:12:26.03,1:12:28.03,Default,,0,0,0,,the monkeys, the gorilla
Dialogue: 0,1:12:28.03,1:12:31.31,Default,,0,0,0,,chimpanzees
Dialogue: 0,1:12:31.31,1:12:33.31,Default,,0,0,0,,cocos, the trained gorilla
Dialogue: 0,1:12:33.31,1:12:36.51,Default,,0,0,0,,calibrates at 405
Dialogue: 0,1:12:36.51,1:12:38.51,Default,,0,0,0,,you are very safe in a cage
Dialogue: 0,1:12:38.51,1:12:40.51,Default,,0,0,0,,of a gorilla
Dialogue: 0,1:12:40.51,1:12:42.51,Default,,0,0,0,,and you are not safe with 85%
Dialogue: 0,1:12:42.51,1:12:44.51,Default,,0,0,0,,of humans alive today
Dialogue: 0,1:12:44.51,1:12:47.63,Default,,0,0,0,,coco will not hurt you at all
Dialogue: 0,1:12:47.63,1:12:49.65,Default,,0,0,0,,coco will be happy
Dialogue: 0,1:12:49.65,1:12:51.65,Default,,0,0,0,,so you can teach coco words
Dialogue: 0,1:12:51.65,1:12:54.43,Default,,0,0,0,,and the two most
Dialogue: 0,1:12:54.43,1:12:56.43,Default,,0,0,0,,amazing things
Dialogue: 0,1:12:56.43,1:12:58.43,Default,,0,0,0,,are the cats
Dialogue: 0,1:12:58.43,1:13:00.75,Default,,0,0,0,,the cat's purr
Dialogue: 0,1:13:00.75,1:13:02.75,Default,,0,0,0,,is at 500
Dialogue: 0,1:13:02.75,1:13:04.84,Default,,0,0,0,,and the dog's wagging tail is at 500
Dialogue: 0,1:13:04.84,1:13:06.84,Default,,0,0,0,,they are man's best friends
Dialogue: 0,1:13:08.84,1:13:11.52,Default,,0,0,0,,why is that?
Dialogue: 0,1:13:11.52,1:13:13.57,Default,,0,0,0,,because they respond to essence
Dialogue: 0,1:13:13.57,1:13:15.57,Default,,0,0,0,,we've got a new kitty at home
Dialogue: 0,1:13:15.57,1:13:17.64,Default,,0,0,0,,and when I come over
Dialogue: 0,1:13:17.64,1:13:19.64,Default,,0,0,0,,and I merely intend
Dialogue: 0,1:13:19.64,1:13:21.64,Default,,0,0,0,,to start petting the kitty
Dialogue: 0,1:13:21.64,1:13:23.64,Default,,0,0,0,,it instantly starts to purr
Dialogue: 0,1:13:23.64,1:13:25.64,Default,,0,0,0,,it's like you can turn it on a long distance
Dialogue: 0,1:13:25.64,1:13:27.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I come in like this
Dialogue: 0,1:13:27.64,1:13:29.64,Default,,0,0,0,,and I think of kitty
Dialogue: 0,1:13:29.64,1:13:31.64,Default,,0,0,0,,and I think of petting kitty
Dialogue: 0,1:13:31.64,1:13:33.64,Default,,0,0,0,,and the girls in the office will say
Dialogue: 0,1:13:33.64,1:13:35.64,Default,,0,0,0,,he's purring already
Dialogue: 0,1:13:35.64,1:13:38.31,Default,,0,0,0,,and of course the dog
Dialogue: 0,1:13:38.31,1:13:40.31,Default,,0,0,0,,instantly knows
Dialogue: 0,1:13:40.31,1:13:42.96,Default,,0,0,0,,when I treated lots and lots of patients
Dialogue: 0,1:13:42.96,1:13:44.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I had a lot
Dialogue: 0,1:13:44.96,1:13:46.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I practiced 50 years
Dialogue: 0,1:13:46.96,1:13:48.96,Default,,0,0,0,,and I would have depressed people
Dialogue: 0,1:13:48.96,1:13:50.96,Default,,0,0,0,,living alone
Dialogue: 0,1:13:50.96,1:13:54.77,Default,,0,0,0,,and I told them if you don't get a dog or a cat
Dialogue: 0,1:13:54.77,1:13:56.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't treat you
Dialogue: 0,1:13:56.77,1:13:58.77,Default,,0,0,0,,no, because that person is so narcissistic
Dialogue: 0,1:13:58.77,1:14:01.03,Default,,0,0,0,,they can't even take care of a pet
Dialogue: 0,1:14:01.03,1:14:03.03,Default,,0,0,0,,there is no way they are going to heal
Dialogue: 0,1:14:03.03,1:14:05.03,Default,,0,0,0,,they are going to sit there and wallow
Dialogue: 0,1:14:05.03,1:14:07.39,Default,,0,0,0,,in their narcissistic self indulgent grief
Dialogue: 0,1:14:07.39,1:14:09.39,Default,,0,0,0,,and resentment and self pity
Dialogue: 0,1:14:09.39,1:14:12.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I said well I'll treat you if you get a dog
Dialogue: 0,1:14:12.06,1:14:14.06,Default,,0,0,0,,one lady said no
Dialogue: 0,1:14:14.06,1:14:16.76,Default,,0,0,0,,she hated dogs
Dialogue: 0,1:14:16.76,1:14:19.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I said you'll have to find another doctor
Dialogue: 0,1:14:19.88,1:14:21.88,Default,,0,0,0,,that's a fact
Dialogue: 0,1:14:21.88,1:14:23.88,Default,,0,0,0,,the incapacity, the refusal to love
Dialogue: 0,1:14:23.88,1:14:25.88,Default,,0,0,0,,and the refusal of love
Dialogue: 0,1:14:25.88,1:14:27.97,Default,,0,0,0,,in its most appealing form
Dialogue: 0,1:14:27.97,1:14:29.97,Default,,0,0,0,,means such a degree of narcissism
Dialogue: 0,1:14:29.97,1:14:31.97,Default,,0,0,0,,and selfishness
Dialogue: 0,1:14:31.97,1:14:33.97,Default,,0,0,0,,that you're not going to be able to relate
Dialogue: 0,1:14:33.97,1:14:35.97,Default,,0,0,0,,so because part of helping a patient
Dialogue: 0,1:14:35.97,1:14:37.97,Default,,0,0,0,,is a positive transference
Dialogue: 0,1:14:37.97,1:14:39.97,Default,,0,0,0,,faith in the energy that you put forth for them
Dialogue: 0,1:14:39.97,1:14:41.97,Default,,0,0,0,,they're not going to form a positive transference
Dialogue: 0,1:14:41.97,1:14:44.75,Default,,0,0,0,,with you
Dialogue: 0,1:14:44.75,1:14:46.75,Default,,0,0,0,,if they're not going to care about a vibing dog
Dialogue: 0,1:14:46.75,1:14:48.84,Default,,0,0,0,,they're not going to care about you
Dialogue: 0,1:14:48.84,1:14:50.84,Default,,0,0,0,,so one of the levers you have to get patients better
Dialogue: 0,1:14:50.84,1:14:52.84,Default,,0,0,0,,is the transference
Dialogue: 0,1:14:52.84,1:14:55.06,Default,,0,0,0,,and of course you use it
Dialogue: 0,1:14:55.06,1:14:57.06,Default,,0,0,0,,and the transference is
Dialogue: 0,1:14:57.06,1:14:59.06,Default,,0,0,0,,one of the things that's non-linear
Dialogue: 0,1:14:59.06,1:15:01.06,Default,,0,0,0,,so
Dialogue: 0,1:15:01.06,1:15:03.06,Default,,0,0,0,,scientific inquiry
Dialogue: 0,1:15:03.06,1:15:05.06,Default,,0,0,0,,is a lot of it is quite skeptical
Dialogue: 0,1:15:05.06,1:15:07.19,Default,,0,0,0,,and frankly rather dumb
Dialogue: 0,1:15:07.19,1:15:09.19,Default,,0,0,0,,and it's because
Dialogue: 0,1:15:09.19,1:15:11.19,Default,,0,0,0,,it confines itself to the
Dialogue: 0,1:15:11.19,1:15:13.47,Default,,0,0,0,,linear domain
Dialogue: 0,1:15:13.47,1:15:15.47,Default,,0,0,0,,it has to do with the non-linear
Dialogue: 0,1:15:15.47,1:15:17.47,Default,,0,0,0,,it has to do with context
Dialogue: 0,1:15:17.47,1:15:19.47,Default,,0,0,0,,so reality has to do with essence
Dialogue: 0,1:15:19.47,1:15:21.47,Default,,0,0,0,,which has to do with context
Dialogue: 0,1:15:21.47,1:15:23.47,Default,,0,0,0,,and the trouble with the scoffer and the skeptic
Dialogue: 0,1:15:23.47,1:15:25.47,Default,,0,0,0,,is they're sticking to low levels of
Dialogue: 0,1:15:25.47,1:15:27.47,Default,,0,0,0,,mentation
Dialogue: 0,1:15:27.47,1:15:29.47,Default,,0,0,0,,and they're sticking to just the
Dialogue: 0,1:15:29.47,1:15:31.64,Default,,0,0,0,,linear pedestrian level
Dialogue: 0,1:15:31.64,1:15:33.64,Default,,0,0,0,,so that's the story on animals
Dialogue: 0,1:15:33.64,1:15:35.71,Default,,0,0,0,,and
Dialogue: 0,1:15:35.71,1:15:37.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I think it's quite interesting
Dialogue: 0,1:15:37.71,1:15:39.71,Default,,0,0,0,,we have an African parrot at home
Dialogue: 0,1:15:39.71,1:15:41.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Dr. Kalmbach gave it to me
Dialogue: 0,1:15:41.71,1:15:43.73,Default,,0,0,0,,where is
Dialogue: 0,1:15:43.73,1:15:45.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Broccoli
Dialogue: 0,1:15:45.77,1:15:47.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Broccoli's consciousness level
Dialogue: 0,1:15:47.77,1:15:49.80,Default,,0,0,0,,is currently over 350
Dialogue: 0,1:15:49.80,1:15:52.25,Default,,0,0,0,,370
Dialogue: 0,1:15:52.25,1:15:54.25,Default,,0,0,0,,365
Dialogue: 0,1:15:54.25,1:15:56.56,Default,,0,0,0,,she's up to 365
Dialogue: 0,1:15:56.56,1:15:58.56,Default,,0,0,0,,she ain't the brightest bird on the planet
Dialogue: 0,1:15:58.56,1:16:00.56,Default,,0,0,0,,but
Dialogue: 0,1:16:03.21,1:16:05.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Susan teaches her
Dialogue: 0,1:16:05.21,1:16:07.21,Default,,0,0,0,,funny songs all the time
Dialogue: 0,1:16:07.21,1:16:09.23,Default,,0,0,0,,what are you teaching her now
Dialogue: 0,1:16:09.23,1:16:11.39,Default,,0,0,0,,jingle bells, she's teaching her jingle bells
Dialogue: 0,1:16:13.39,1:16:15.39,Default,,0,0,0,,so we'll go to the next one
Dialogue: 0,1:16:15.39,1:16:17.88,Default,,0,0,0,,the great books of the world
Dialogue: 0,1:16:17.88,1:16:19.88,Default,,0,0,0,,so we were talking about
Dialogue: 0,1:16:19.88,1:16:21.88,Default,,0,0,0,,what is the significance of the level
Dialogue: 0,1:16:21.88,1:16:23.88,Default,,0,0,0,,this is the 400s
Dialogue: 0,1:16:23.88,1:16:25.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to watch the time
Dialogue: 0,1:16:25.88,1:16:28.75,Default,,0,0,0,,what time do we have to take a break
Dialogue: 0,1:16:28.75,1:16:30.75,Default,,0,0,0,,this is going to cover centuries
Dialogue: 0,1:16:30.75,1:16:32.75,Default,,0,0,0,,of the world's greatest wisdom
Dialogue: 0,1:16:32.75,1:16:35.03,Default,,0,0,0,,it'll only take us a few minutes
Dialogue: 0,1:16:35.03,1:16:37.13,Default,,0,0,0,,it's called
Dialogue: 0,1:16:37.13,1:16:39.52,Default,,0,0,0,,the great books of the western world
Dialogue: 0,1:16:39.52,1:16:41.52,Default,,0,0,0,,this is what I grew up
Dialogue: 0,1:16:41.52,1:16:43.52,Default,,0,0,0,,to think is a liberal education
Dialogue: 0,1:16:43.52,1:16:45.52,Default,,0,0,0,,a liberal education
Dialogue: 0,1:16:45.52,1:16:47.52,Default,,0,0,0,,is one in which
Dialogue: 0,1:16:47.52,1:16:49.52,Default,,0,0,0,,you discover
Dialogue: 0,1:16:49.52,1:16:51.52,Default,,0,0,0,,this is the content of your college education
Dialogue: 0,1:16:51.52,1:16:54.80,Default,,0,0,0,,that you're at least familiar
Dialogue: 0,1:16:54.80,1:16:56.80,Default,,0,0,0,,with the gist, the thrust
Dialogue: 0,1:16:56.80,1:16:58.80,Default,,0,0,0,,the impact
Dialogue: 0,1:16:58.80,1:17:01.05,Default,,0,0,0,,you get
Dialogue: 0,1:17:01.05,1:17:03.05,Default,,0,0,0,,you get the levels of truth
Dialogue: 0,1:17:03.05,1:17:05.11,Default,,0,0,0,,the levels of
Dialogue: 0,1:17:05.11,1:17:07.11,Default,,0,0,0,,contextualization
Dialogue: 0,1:17:07.11,1:17:09.11,Default,,0,0,0,,and you don't make
Dialogue: 0,1:17:09.11,1:17:11.11,Default,,0,0,0,,foolish statements
Dialogue: 0,1:17:11.11,1:17:13.11,Default,,0,0,0,,the world right now is full of relativists
Dialogue: 0,1:17:13.11,1:17:15.11,Default,,0,0,0,,who all calibrate at 190
Dialogue: 0,1:17:15.11,1:17:17.11,Default,,0,0,0,,and they can't even stay with one single subject
Dialogue: 0,1:17:17.11,1:17:20.93,Default,,0,0,0,,you know
Dialogue: 0,1:17:20.93,1:17:22.93,Default,,0,0,0,,they can't stay
Dialogue: 0,1:17:22.93,1:17:24.93,Default,,0,0,0,,within the same category of thought
Dialogue: 0,1:17:24.93,1:17:26.93,Default,,0,0,0,,so here's the greatest names
Dialogue: 0,1:17:26.93,1:17:28.93,Default,,0,0,0,,in all of
Dialogue: 0,1:17:28.93,1:17:30.93,Default,,0,0,0,,recent history
Dialogue: 0,1:17:30.93,1:17:32.93,Default,,0,0,0,,you see Darwin is at 450
Dialogue: 0,1:17:32.93,1:17:34.93,Default,,0,0,0,,so
Dialogue: 0,1:17:34.93,1:17:36.93,Default,,0,0,0,,this is the level of causality
Dialogue: 0,1:17:36.93,1:17:39.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Descartes
Dialogue: 0,1:17:39.71,1:17:41.71,Default,,0,0,0,,who I quote quite a bit
Dialogue: 0,1:17:41.71,1:17:43.71,Default,,0,0,0,,is at 490
Dialogue: 0,1:17:43.71,1:17:45.86,Default,,0,0,0,,he differentiated
Dialogue: 0,1:17:45.86,1:17:47.86,Default,,0,0,0,,the difference between appearance
Dialogue: 0,1:17:47.86,1:17:49.86,Default,,0,0,0,,and reality
Dialogue: 0,1:17:49.86,1:17:51.86,Default,,0,0,0,,the difference between appearance and essence
Dialogue: 0,1:17:51.86,1:17:53.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Immanuel Kant
Dialogue: 0,1:17:53.86,1:17:55.86,Default,,0,0,0,,all the great names here
Dialogue: 0,1:17:55.86,1:17:58.06,Default,,0,0,0,,are in the mid 400s
Dialogue: 0,1:17:58.06,1:18:00.06,Default,,0,0,0,,this I happen to have
Dialogue: 0,1:18:00.06,1:18:02.06,Default,,0,0,0,,a set which I picked up at a very good buy
Dialogue: 0,1:18:02.06,1:18:04.06,Default,,0,0,0,,there's only two things wrong with it
Dialogue: 0,1:18:04.06,1:18:06.06,Default,,0,0,0,,you see
Dialogue: 0,1:18:06.06,1:18:08.06,Default,,0,0,0,,the average is about 450 to 460
Dialogue: 0,1:18:08.06,1:18:10.06,Default,,0,0,0,,suddenly you see
Dialogue: 0,1:18:10.06,1:18:12.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Karl Marx at 130
Dialogue: 0,1:18:12.06,1:18:14.06,Default,,0,0,0,,there you see the introduction of relativism
Dialogue: 0,1:18:14.06,1:18:16.06,Default,,0,0,0,,and its impact in the modern world
Dialogue: 0,1:18:16.06,1:18:18.06,Default,,0,0,0,,historically we see the impact of
Dialogue: 0,1:18:18.06,1:18:20.06,Default,,0,0,0,,calibrated 130
Dialogue: 0,1:18:20.06,1:18:22.06,Default,,0,0,0,,you know
Dialogue: 0,1:18:22.06,1:18:24.06,Default,,0,0,0,,a million Chinese die of starvation
Dialogue: 0,1:18:24.06,1:18:26.06,Default,,0,0,0,,etc
Dialogue: 0,1:18:26.06,1:18:28.06,Default,,0,0,0,,we see the fallacy of low 130
Dialogue: 0,1:18:28.06,1:18:30.06,Default,,0,0,0,,if you try to institute it as a political
Dialogue: 0,1:18:30.06,1:18:32.18,Default,,0,0,0,,social
Dialogue: 0,1:18:32.18,1:18:34.82,Default,,0,0,0,,legal reality
Dialogue: 0,1:18:34.82,1:18:36.82,Default,,0,0,0,,and he wrote it with Engels
Dialogue: 0,1:18:36.82,1:18:38.82,Default,,0,0,0,,who was at 200
Dialogue: 0,1:18:38.82,1:18:40.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Engels just didn't know any better
Dialogue: 0,1:18:40.82,1:18:42.82,Default,,0,0,0,,at 200 he thought Marx sounded good
Dialogue: 0,1:18:42.82,1:18:45.94,Default,,0,0,0,,so he went along with it
Dialogue: 0,1:18:45.94,1:18:47.97,Default,,0,0,0,,but here's the great minds of history
Dialogue: 0,1:18:47.97,1:18:49.97,Default,,0,0,0,,so
Dialogue: 0,1:18:49.97,1:18:51.97,Default,,0,0,0,,to argue with
Dialogue: 0,1:18:51.97,1:18:53.97,Default,,0,0,0,,absolutism then
Dialogue: 0,1:18:53.97,1:18:55.97,Default,,0,0,0,,arguments would have to start
Dialogue: 0,1:18:55.97,1:18:58.03,Default,,0,0,0,,around the mid 400s
Dialogue: 0,1:18:58.03,1:19:00.03,Default,,0,0,0,,because all the
Dialogue: 0,1:19:00.03,1:19:02.03,Default,,0,0,0,,philosophic discussions of today's
Dialogue: 0,1:19:02.03,1:19:04.03,Default,,0,0,0,,news etc
Dialogue: 0,1:19:04.03,1:19:06.03,Default,,0,0,0,,so called postmodern relativism etc
Dialogue: 0,1:19:06.03,1:19:08.03,Default,,0,0,0,,you know
Dialogue: 0,1:19:08.03,1:19:10.03,Default,,0,0,0,,is about a 190
Dialogue: 0,1:19:10.03,1:19:12.90,Default,,0,0,0,,you can't even argue with
Dialogue: 0,1:19:12.90,1:19:14.90,Default,,0,0,0,,with absolutism
Dialogue: 0,1:19:14.90,1:19:16.90,Default,,0,0,0,,until you start coming from
Dialogue: 0,1:19:16.90,1:19:18.90,Default,,0,0,0,,an argument that calibrates at least
Dialogue: 0,1:19:18.90,1:19:20.90,Default,,0,0,0,,450 or 460
Dialogue: 0,1:19:20.90,1:19:22.90,Default,,0,0,0,,so we'll go to the next slide
Dialogue: 0,1:19:22.90,1:19:25.47,Default,,0,0,0,,most of the arguments
Dialogue: 0,1:19:25.47,1:19:27.47,Default,,0,0,0,,of the modern world
Dialogue: 0,1:19:27.47,1:19:29.47,Default,,0,0,0,,were settled in about 350 BC
Dialogue: 0,1:19:29.47,1:19:32.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know what happened
Dialogue: 0,1:19:32.25,1:19:34.25,Default,,0,0,0,,in schooling that they haven't learned that
Dialogue: 0,1:19:34.25,1:19:36.53,Default,,0,0,0,,everything that they're studying there
Dialogue: 0,1:19:36.53,1:19:38.53,Default,,0,0,0,,was settled
Dialogue: 0,1:19:38.53,1:19:40.98,Default,,0,0,0,,about 350 BC
Dialogue: 0,1:19:40.98,1:19:43.07,Default,,0,0,0,,somehow
Dialogue: 0,1:19:43.07,1:19:47.55,Default,,0,0,0,,they haven't gotten the word
Dialogue: 0,1:19:47.55,1:19:49.71,Default,,0,0,0,,this is the
Dialogue: 0,1:19:49.71,1:19:52.38,Default,,0,0,0,,context
Dialogue: 0,1:19:52.38,1:19:54.38,Default,,0,0,0,,this is the content
Dialogue: 0,1:19:54.38,1:19:56.98,Default,,0,0,0,,this is approximate field
Dialogue: 0,1:19:56.98,1:19:58.98,Default,,0,0,0,,ok one last slide
Dialogue: 0,1:19:58.98,1:20:01.65,Default,,0,0,0,,and then we stop
Dialogue: 0,1:20:01.65,1:20:03.65,Default,,0,0,0,,the content is the ego
Dialogue: 0,1:20:03.65,1:20:05.65,Default,,0,0,0,,it's linear
Dialogue: 0,1:20:05.65,1:20:07.78,Default,,0,0,0,,this is what we call the ego
Dialogue: 0,1:20:07.78,1:20:09.78,Default,,0,0,0,,in scientific world we say
Dialogue: 0,1:20:09.78,1:20:11.78,Default,,0,0,0,,it's Newtonian world
Dialogue: 0,1:20:11.78,1:20:13.78,Default,,0,0,0,,it's placed in time and location
Dialogue: 0,1:20:13.78,1:20:16.23,Default,,0,0,0,,and it's provable
Dialogue: 0,1:20:16.23,1:20:18.23,Default,,0,0,0,,and if we compare that with
Dialogue: 0,1:20:18.23,1:20:20.23,Default,,0,0,0,,context you see
Dialogue: 0,1:20:20.23,1:20:22.23,Default,,0,0,0,,context is the opposite
Dialogue: 0,1:20:22.23,1:20:24.35,Default,,0,0,0,,it's non-linear it's unlimited
Dialogue: 0,1:20:24.35,1:20:26.35,Default,,0,0,0,,it's spiritual
Dialogue: 0,1:20:26.35,1:20:28.35,Default,,0,0,0,,you can verify it but you can't prove it
Dialogue: 0,1:20:28.35,1:20:30.35,Default,,0,0,0,,you can know it by becoming it
Dialogue: 0,1:20:30.35,1:20:32.35,Default,,0,0,0,,and it's non-local
Dialogue: 0,1:20:32.35,1:20:34.35,Default,,0,0,0,,it's enough to give you a headache
Dialogue: 0,1:20:34.35,1:20:36.35,Default,,0,0,0,,just thinking about all that
Dialogue: 0,1:20:36.35,1:20:38.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry I went into it so much folks
Dialogue: 0,1:20:38.35,1:20:40.35,Default,,0,0,0,,but I just had to do it
Dialogue: 0,1:20:40.35,1:20:42.35,Default,,0,0,0,,you know because
Dialogue: 0,1:20:42.35,1:20:44.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I have a certain obsessive impulsive
Dialogue: 0,1:20:44.35,1:20:46.35,Default,,0,0,0,,academic trend
Dialogue: 0,1:20:46.35,1:20:48.35,Default,,0,0,0,,that I'm struggling to overcome
Dialogue: 0,1:20:48.35,1:20:51.06,Default,,0,0,0,,but I feel an obligation
Dialogue: 0,1:20:51.06,1:20:53.06,Default,,0,0,0,,there are actually real intellectuals
Dialogue: 0,1:20:53.06,1:20:55.06,Default,,0,0,0,,out there who are actually
Dialogue: 0,1:20:55.06,1:20:57.06,Default,,0,0,0,,legitimately interested in finding truth
Dialogue: 0,1:20:57.06,1:20:59.06,Default,,0,0,0,,for its own sake
Dialogue: 0,1:20:59.06,1:21:01.06,Default,,0,0,0,,and therefore for their sake
Dialogue: 0,1:21:01.06,1:21:03.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I say those things so that I can sleep well
Dialogue: 0,1:21:03.06,1:21:16.68,Default,,0,0,0,,how long do we have for a break?
Dialogue: 0,1:21:16.68,1:21:18.68,Default,,0,0,0,,we'll be back in about
Dialogue: 0,1:21:18.68,1:21:20.68,Default,,0,0,0,,15-20 minutes
